ka hii.','The temporary backup directory exists but is not writable'=>'Saraka ya chelezo ya muda ipo lakini haiwezi kuandikwa','The %s directory exists but is not writable. This directory is used to improve the stability of theme updates. Please make sure the server has write permissions to this directory.'=>'Saraka %s ipo lakini haiwezi kuandikwa. Saraka hii inatumika kuboresha uthabiti wa masasisho ya mandhari. Tafadhali hakikisha kuwa seva ina ruhusa za kuandikwa kwenye saraka hii.','Theme temporary backup directory exists but is not writable'=>'Saraka ya hifadhi ya muda ya mandhari ipo lakini haiwezi kuandikwa','The %s directory exists but is not writable. This directory is used to improve the stability of plugin updates. Please make sure the server has write permissions to this directory.'=>'Saraka %s ipo lakini haiwezi kuandikwa. Saraka hii inatumika kuboresha uthabiti wa masasisho ya programu-jalizi. Tafadhali hakikisha kuwa seva ina ruhusa za kuandikwa kwenye saraka hii.','Plugin temporary backup directory exists but is not writable'=>'Saraka ya chelezo ya muda ya programu-jalizi ipo lakini haiwezi kuandikwa','The %1$s and %2$s directories exist but are not writable. These directories are used to improve the stability of plugin updates. Please make sure the server has write permissions to these directories.'=>'Saraka za %1$s na %2$s zipo lakini haziandikiki. Saraka hizi hutumiwa kuboresha uthabiti wa masasisho ya programu-jalizi. Tafadhali hakikisha seva ina ruhusa za kuandika kwa saraka hizi.','Plugin and theme temporary backup directories exist but are not writable'=>'Saraka za chelezo za muda za programu-jalizi na mandhari zipo lakini haziwezi kuandikwa','The %s directory cannot be located.'=>'Saraka %s haipatikani.','The %s directory used to improve the stability of plugin and theme updates is writable.'=>'Saraka %s inayotumika kuboresha uthabiti wa programu-jalizi na masasisho ya mandhari inaweza kuandikwa.','Plugin and theme temporary backup directory is writable'=>'Programu-jalizi na saraka ya chelezo ya muda ya mandhari inaweza kuandikwa','Could not determine available disk space for updates.'=>'Haikuweza kubainisha nafasi inayopatikana ya diski kwa masasisho.','Available disk space is critically low, less than %s available. Proceed with caution, updates may fail.'=>'Nafasi ya diski inayopatikana iko chini sana, chini ya %s inapatikana. Endelea kwa tahadhari, masasisho yanaweza kushindwa.','Available disk space is low, less than %s available.'=>'Nafasi ya diski inayopatikana ni ndogo, chini ya %s inapatikana.','%s available disk space was detected, update routines can be performed safely.'=>'%s nafasi ya diski inayopatikana imegunduliwa, taratibu za kusasisha zinaweza kufanywa kwa usalama.','Disk space available to safely perform updates'=>'Nafasi ya diski inapatikana ili kufanya masasisho kwa usalama','Table ordered by Hierarchical Menu Order and Title.'=>'Jedwali limepangwa kwa Agizo la Menyu ya Hierarkia na Kichwa.','Table ordered by Title.'=>'Jedwali lililopangwa kwa jina.','Table ordered by Date.'=>'Jedwali lililopangwa kwa tarehe.','Table ordered by Comments.'=>'Jedwali lililopangwa kwa maoni.','Table ordered by Uploaded To.'=>'Jedwali limepangwa kwa Imepakiwa Kwa.','Table ordered by Author.'=>'Jedwali lilipangwa kwa Mwandishi.','Table ordered by File Name.'=>'Jedwali limepangwa kwa Jina la Faili.','Descending.'=>'Kushuka.','Ascending.'=>'Kupanda.','Sort descending.'=>'Panga kwa kushuka','Sort ascending.'=>'Panga kwa kupanda.','Table ordered by Rating.'=>'Jedwali lililopangwa kwa ukadiriaji.','Table ordered by Visibility.'=>'Jedwali lililopangwa kwa Kuonekana.','Table ordered by URL.'=>'Jedwali lililopangwa kwa kiungo.','Table ordered by Name.'=>'Jedwali lililopangwa kwa Jina.','Current Server time'=>'Wakati wa sasa wa Seva','Current UTC time'=>'Saa ya sasa ya UTC','Current time'=>'Saa ya sasa','Ordered by Comment Date, descending.'=>'Imepangwa kwa Tarehe ya Maoni, kushuka.','Table ordered by Post Replied To.'=>'Jedwali lililoagizwa na Chapisho Lililojibiwa Kwa.','Table ordered by Comment Author.'=>'Jedwali limeagizwa na Mwandishi wa Maoni.','Attempting to restore the previous version.'=>'Inajaribu kurejesha toleo la awali.','More details.'=>'Maelezo zaidi','Find your team &rarr;'=>'Tafuta timu yako &rarr;','Finding the area that aligns with your skills and interests is the first step toward meaningful contribution. With more than 20 Make WordPress teams working on different parts of the open source WordPress project, there&#8217;s a place for everyone, no matter what your skill set is.'=>'Kupata eneo ambalo linalingana na ujuzi na mambo yanayokuvutia ni hatua ya kwanza kuelekea mchango wa maana. Kwa zaidi ya timu 20 za Fanya WordPress zinazofanya kazi kwenye sehemu tofauti za mradi wa WordPress wa chanzo huria, kuna&#8217; mahali pa kila mtu, bila kujali seti yako ya ujuzi ni nini.','Shape the future of the web with WordPress'=>'Tengeneza mustakabali wa wavuti ukitumia WordPress','WordPress app: Kotlin, Java, Swift, Objective-C, Vue, Python, and TypeScript.'=>'Programu ya WordPress: Kotlin, Java, Swift, Objective-C, Vue, Python, na TypeScript.','WordPress Core and Block Editor: HTML, CSS, PHP, SQL, JavaScript, and React.'=>'Kihariri cha Msingi na Bloku cha WordPress: HTML, CSS, PHP, SQL, JavaScript, na React.','WordPress embraces new technologies, while being committed to backward compatibility. The WordPress project uses the following languages and libraries:'=>'WordPress inakumbatia teknolojia mpya, huku ikiwa imejitolea kwa utangamano wa nyuma. Mradi wa WordPress hutumia lugha na maktaba zifuatazo:','<strong>Contribute</strong> to the code, improve the UX, and test the WordPress app.'=>'<strong>Changia</strong> kwa msimbo, boresha UX, na ujaribu programu ya WordPress.','<strong>Write</strong> and submit patches to fix bugs or help build new features.'=>'<strong>Andika</strong> na uwasilishe viraka ili kurekebisha hitilafu au kusaidia kuunda vipengele vipya.','<strong>Test</strong> new releases and proposed features for the Block Editor.'=>'<strong>Jaribio</strong> matoleo mapya na vipengele vilivyopendekezwa vya Kihariri cha Kuzuia.','<strong>Find</strong> and report bugs in the WordPress core software.'=>'<strong>Tafuta</strong> na uripoti hitilafu katika programu ya msingi ya WordPress.','If you do code, or want to learn how, you can contribute technically in numerous ways:'=>'Kama unandika kanuni, au unataka kujifunza jinsi gani, unaweza kuchangia kiufundi kwa njia nyingi:','Code-based contribution'=>'Changia kwa ukokotozi','<strong>Explore</strong> ways to reduce the environmental impact of websites.'=>'<strong>Gundua</strong> njia za kupunguza athari za mazingira za tovuti.','<strong>Edit</strong> videos and add captions to WordPress.tv.'=>'<strong>Hariri</strong> video na uongeze maelezo mafupi kwenye WordPress.tv.','<strong>Lend</strong> your creative imagination to the WordPress UI design.'=>'<strong>Azima</strong> mawazo yako ya ubunifu kwa muundo wa WordPress UI.','<strong>Organize</strong> or participate in local Meetups and WordCamps.'=>'<strong>Panga</strong> au ushiriki katika Mikutano ya ndani na WordCamps.','<strong>Curate</strong> submissions or take photos for the Photo Directory.'=>'<strong>Rekebisha</strong> mawasilisho au piga picha kwa Orodha ya Picha.','<strong>Promote</strong> the WordPress project to your community.'=>'<strong>Kuza</strong> mradi wa WordPress kwa jumuiya yako.','<strong>Create</strong> and improve WordPress educational materials.'=>'<strong>Unda</strong> na uboresha nyenzo za kielimu za WordPress.','<strong>Translate</strong> WordPress into your local language.'=>'<strong>Tafsiri</strong> WordPress katika lugha yako ya ndani.','<strong>Write</strong> or improve documentation for WordPress.'=>'<strong>Andika</strong> au uboresha hati za WordPress.','<strong>Share</strong> your knowledge in the WordPress support forums.'=>'<strong>Shiriki</strong> maarifa yako katika mijadala ya usaidizi ya WordPress.','WordPress may thrive on technical contributions, but you don&#8217;t have to code to contribute. Here are some of the ways you can make an impact without writing a single line of code:'=>'WordPress kustawi kwa michango ya mwongozo, lakini huhitaji&#8217; kuweka msimbo ili kuchangia. Hapa kuna baadhi ya njia unazoweza kuleta athari bila kuandika safu moja ya nambari:','No-code contribution'=>'Kuchangia bila kukokotoa','Grow your network and make friends.'=>'Kuza mtandao wako na upate marafiki.','Apply your skills or learn new ones.'=>'Tumia ujuzi wako au ujifunze mpya.','Be part of a global open source community.'=>'Kuwa sehemu ya jumuiya ya kimataifa ya chanzo huria.','Join the diverse WordPress contributor community and connect with other people who are passionate about maintaining a free and open web.'=>'Jiunge na jumuiya mbalimbali za wachangiaji wa WordPress na uungane na watu wengine ambao wana shauku ya kudumisha mtandao wazi na bure.','Do you use WordPress for work, for personal projects, or even just for fun? You can help shape the long-term success of the open source project that powers millions of websites around the world.'=>'Je, unatumia WordPress kwa kazi, kwa miradi ya kibinafsi, au hata kwa kujifurahisha tu? Unaweza kusaidia kuunda mafanikio ya muda mrefu ya mradi wa programu huria unaowezesha mamilioni ya tovuti kote ulimwenguni.','Be the future of WordPress'=>'Kuwa mustakabali wa WordPress','<a href="%1$s">Learn WordPress</a> is a free resource for new and experienced WordPress users. Learn is stocked with how-to videos on using various features in WordPress, <a href="%2$s">interactive workshops</a> for exploring topics in-depth, and lesson plans for diving deep into specific areas of WordPress.'=>'<a href="%1$s">Jifunze WordPress</a> ni rasilimali isiyolipishwa kwa watumiaji wapya na wenye uzoefu wa WordPress. Jifunze imejaa video za jinsi ya kutumia vipengele mbalimbali katika WordPress, <a href="%2$s">warsha shirikishi</a> kwa ajili ya kuchunguza mada kwa kina, na mipango ya somo la kuzama katika maeneo mahususi ya WordPress. .','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/forums/">Support forums</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/forums/">Vikao vya msaada</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/appearance-widgets-screen-classic-editor/">Documentation on Widgets</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/appearance-widgets-screen-classic-editor/">Nyaraka kuhusu Wijeti</a>','<strong>View</strong> takes you to a public author archive which lists all the posts published by the user.'=>'<strong>Tazama</strong> inakupeleka kwenye kumbukumbu ya waandishi wa umma ambayo huorodhesha machapisho yote yaliyochapishwa na mtumiaji.','<strong>Download file</strong> downloads the original media file to your device.'=>'<strong>Pakua faili</strong> hupakua faili asili ya midia kwenye kifaa chako.','site editor title tagEditor'=>'Mhariri','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/plugins-themes-auto-updates/">Documentation on Auto-updates</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/plugins-themes-auto-updates/">Hati kuhusu masasisho ya Kiotomatiki</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/customize-date-and-time-format/">Documentation on date and time formatting</a>.'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/customize-date-and-time-format/">Hati kuhusu uumbizaji wa tarehe na saa</a>.','You can set the language, and WordPress will automatically download and install the translation files (available if your filesystem is writable).'=>'Unaweza kuweka lugha, na WordPress itapakua na kusakinisha kiotomatiki faili za tafsiri (zinapatikana ikiwa mfumo wako wa faili unaweza kuandikwa).','If you want site visitors to be able to register themselves, check the membership box. If you want the site administrator to register every new user, leave the box unchecked. In either case, you can set a default user role for all new users.'=>'Ikiwa unataka wanaotembelea tovuti waweze kujiandikisha, chagua kisanduku cha uanachama. Ikiwa unataka msimamizi wa tovuti kusajili kila mtumiaji mpya, acha kisanduku bila kuchaguliwa. Kwa vyovyote vile, unaweza kuweka jukumu la mtumiaji chaguo-msingi kwa watumiaji wote wapya.','Both WordPress URL and site URL can start with either %1$s or %2$s. A URL starting with %2$s requires an SSL certificate, so be sure that you have one before changing to %2$s. With %2$s, a padlock will appear next to the address in the browser address bar. Both %2$s and the padlock signal that your site meets some basic security requirements, which can build trust with your visitors and with search engines.'=>'URL ya WordPress na URL ya tovuti zinaweza kuanza na %1$s au %2$s. URL inayoanza na %2$s inahitaji cheti cha SSL, kwa hivyo hakikisha kuwa unayo kabla ya kubadilisha hadi %2$s. Na %2$s, kufuli itaonekana karibu na anwani katika upau wa anwani wa kivinjari. %2$s na kufuli huashiria kwamba tovuti yako inakidhi mahitaji ya kimsingi ya usalama, ambayo yanaweza kujenga uaminifu kwa wageni wako na injini za utafutaji.','Though the terms refer to two different concepts, in practice, they can be the same address or different. For example, you can have the core WordPress installation files in the root directory (<code>https://example.com</code>), in which case the two URLs would be the same. Or the <a href="%s">WordPress files can be in a subdirectory</a> (<code>https://example.com/wordpress</code>). In that case, the WordPress URL and the site URL would be different.'=>'Ingawa maneno hurejelea dhana mbili tofauti, kiutendaji, zinaweza kuwa anwani sawa au tofauti. Kwa mfano, unaweza kuwa na faili za msingi za usakinishaji za WordPress kwenye saraka ya mizizi (<code>https://example.com</code>), ambapo URL hizo mbili zitakuwa sawa. Au <a href="%s">faili za WordPress zinaweza kuwa katika saraka ndogo</a> (<code>https://example.com/wordpress</code>). Katika hali hiyo, URL ya WordPress na URL ya tovuti itakuwa tofauti.','Two terms you will want to know are the WordPress URL and the site URL. The WordPress URL is where the core WordPress installation files are, and the site URL is the address a visitor uses in the browser to go to your site.'=>'Masharti mawili ambayo utataka kujua ni URL ya WordPress na URL ya tovuti. URL ya WordPress ndipo faili kuu za usakinishaji za WordPress ziko, na URL ya tovuti ni anwani anayotumia mgeni kwenye kivinjari kwenda kwenye tovuti yako.','RoboHash (Generated)'=>'RoboHash (Imetolewa)','site editor menu itemEditor'=>'Kihariri','Allow <a href="%s">trackbacks and pingbacks</a>'=>'Ruhusu <a href="%s">trackbacks na pingbacks</a>','https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/assign-custom-fields/'=>'https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/assign-custom-fields/','https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/what-is-an-excerpt-classic-editor/'=>'https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/what-is-an-excerpt-classic-editor/','%s expects a non-empty string.'=>'%s inatarajia mfuatano usio tupu.','The destination directory already exists and could not be removed.'=>'Saraka lengwa tayari ipo na haikuweza kuondolewa.','The destination folder already exists.'=>'Folda lengwa tayari lipo.','The source and destination are the same.'=>'Chanzo na marudio ni sawa.','Expand or collapse the elements by clicking on their headings, and arrange them by dragging their headings or by clicking on the up and down arrows.'=>'Panua au ukunje vipengele kwa kubofya vichwa vyao, na uvipange kwa kuburuta vichwa vyao au kwa kubofya mishale ya juu na chini.','Download &#8220;%s&#8221;'=>'Pakua &#8220;%s&#8221;','The "%s" argument must be a non-empty string.'=>'Hoja ya "%s" lazima iwe mfuatano usio tupu.','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/write-posts-classic-editor/">Documentation on Writing and Editing Posts</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/write-posts-classic-editor/">Hati kuhusu Kuandika na Kuhariri Machapisho</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/keyboard-shortcuts-classic-editor/#keyboard-shortcuts-for-comments">Documentation on Keyboard Shortcuts</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/keyboard-shortcuts-classic-editor/#keyboard-shortcuts-for-comments">Kuweka Hati kwenye Njia za Mkato za Kibodi</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/understand-comment-spam/">Documentation on Comment Spam</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/understand-comment-spam/">Nyaraka kuhusu Barua Taka ya Maoni</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/customizer/">Documentation on Customizer</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/customizer/">Hati kuhusu Kibinafsishaji</a>','https://wordpress.org/download/'=>'https://wordpress.org/download/','This is the final release of WordPress %s'=>'Hili ndilo toleo la mwisho la WordPress %s','Site Editor'=>'Kihariri wa Tovuti','<strong>Send password reset</strong> sends the user an email with a link to set a new password.'=>'<strong>Weka nywila upya</strong> itatuma barua pepe kwa mtumiaji na nywila mpya.','https://developer.wordpress.org/apis/wp-config-php/#wp-environment-type'=>'https://developer.wordpress.org/apis/wp-config-php/#wp-environment-type','<strong>Copy URL</strong> copies the URL for the media file to your clipboard.'=>'<strong>Nakili URL</strong> hunakili URL ya faili ya midia kwenye ubao wako wa kunakili.','<strong>View</strong> will take you to a public display page for that file.'=>'<strong>Mwonekano</strong> utakupeleka kwenye ukurasa wa maonyesho ya umma wa faili hiyo.','<strong>Delete Permanently</strong> will delete the file from the media library (as well as from any posts to which it is currently attached).'=>'<strong>Futa Kabisa</strong> itafuta faili kutoka kwa maktaba ya midia (pamoja na kutoka kwa machapisho yoyote ambayo imeambatishwa kwa sasa).','<strong>Edit</strong> takes you to a simple screen to edit that individual file&#8217;s metadata. You can also reach that screen by clicking on the media file name or thumbnail.'=>'<strong>Hariri</strong> inakupeleka kwenye skrini rahisi ili kuhariri metadata ya faili hiyo mahususi. Unaweza pia kufikia skrini hiyo kwa kubofya jina la faili ya midia au kijipicha.','Hovering over a row reveals action links that allow you to manage media items. You can perform the following actions:'=>'Kuelea juu ya safu mlalo huonyesha viungo vya vitendo vinavyokuruhusu kudhibiti vipengee vya maudhui. Unaweza kufanya vitendo vifuatavyo:','themesBlock Themes'=>'Mandhari za Bloku','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/block-themes/">Documentation on Block Themes</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/block-themes/">Hati kuhusu Mandhari za Bloku</a>','Block themes'=>'Mandhari za Bloku','With a block theme, you can place and edit blocks without affecting your content by customizing or creating new templates.'=>'Ukiwa na mandhari ya bloku, unaweza kuweka na kuhariri bloku bila kuathiri maudhui yako kwa kubinafsisha au kuunda violezo vipya.','A block theme is a theme that uses blocks for all parts of a site including navigation menus, header, content, and site footer. These themes are built for the features that allow you to edit and customize all parts of your site.'=>'Mandhari ya bloku ni mandhari ambayo hutumia bloku kwa sehemu zote za tovuti ikijumuisha menyu za kusogeza, kichwa, maudhui na kijachini cha tovuti. Mandhari haya yameundwa kwa ajili ya vipengele vinavyokuruhusu kuhariri na kubinafsisha sehemu zote za tovuti yako.','Configuration rules for %s:'=>'Sheria za usanidi za %s:','Customize permalink structure by selecting available tags'=>'Binafsisha muundo wa kiungo cha kudumu kwa kuchagua lebo zinazopatikana','Select the permalink structure for your website. Including the %s tag makes links easy to understand, and can help your posts rank higher in search engines.'=>'Chagua muundo wa kiungo cha tovuti yako. Ikiwa ni pamoja na lebo ya %s hurahisisha viungo kueleweka, na inaweza kusaidia machapisho yako kuwa ya juu zaidi katika injini za utafutaji.','%s removed from permalink structure'=>'%s imeondolewa kwenye muundo wa kiungo cha kudumu','Site Health %s'=>'Hali ya Tovuti %s','Theme Styles & Block Settings'=>'Mitindo ya Mandhari na Mipangilio ya Bloku','The minimum recommended version of PHP is %s.'=>'Toleo la chini kabisa linalopendekezwa la PHP ni %s.','PHP is one of the programming languages used to build WordPress. Newer versions of PHP receive regular security updates and may increase your site&#8217;s performance.'=>'PHP ni mojawapo ya lugha za programu zinazotumiwa kujenga WordPress. Matoleo mapya zaidi ya PHP hupokea masasisho ya mara kwa mara ya usalama na yanaweza kuongeza utendakazi wa tovuti yako&#8217;','Your site is running on an outdated version of PHP (%s), which soon will not be supported by WordPress. Ensure that PHP is updated on your server as soon as possible. Otherwise you will not be able to upgrade WordPress.'=>'Tovuti yako inaendeshwa kwa toleo la zamani la PHP (%s), ambalo hivi karibuni halitatumika na WordPress. Hakikisha kuwa PHP imesasishwa kwenye seva yako haraka iwezekanavyo. Vinginevyo hutaweza kuboresha WordPress.','Your site is running on an outdated version of PHP (%s), which does not receive security updates and soon will not be supported by WordPress. Ensure that PHP is updated on your server as soon as possible. Otherwise you will not be able to upgrade WordPress.'=>'Tovuti yako inaendeshwa kwa toleo la zamani la PHP (%s), ambalo halipokei masasisho ya usalama na hivi karibuni halitaauniwa na WordPress. Hakikisha kuwa PHP imesasishwa kwenye seva yako haraka iwezekanavyo. Vinginevyo hutaweza kuboresha WordPress.','Persistent object cache'=>'Akiba ya kitu kinachoendelea','Page cache'=>'Akiba ya ukurasa','You should use a persistent object cache'=>'Unapaswa kutumia kashe ya kitu kinachoendelea','Your host appears to support the following object caching services: %s.'=>'Mwenyeji wako anaonekana kuauni huduma zifuatazo za kuweka akiba ya kitu: %s.','Your hosting provider can tell you if a persistent object cache can be enabled on your site.'=>'Mtoa huduma wako wa upangishaji anaweza kukuambia ikiwa akiba ya kitu kinachoendelea inaweza kuwashwa kwenye tovuti yako.','A persistent object cache is not required'=>'Akiba inayoendelea ya kitu haihitajiki','Learn more about persistent object caching.'=>'Jifunze zaidi kuhusu uhifadhi wa kipengee endelevu.','A persistent object cache makes your site&#8217;s database more efficient, resulting in faster load times because WordPress can retrieve your site&#8217;s content and settings much more quickly.'=>'Akiba inayoendelea ya kitu hufanya hifadhidata ya tovuti yako kuwa na ufanisi zaidi, hivyo kusababisha nyakati za upakiaji haraka kwa sababu WordPress inaweza kuepua maudhui na mipangilio ya tovuti yako kwa haraka zaidi.','A persistent object cache is being used'=>'Akiba ya kipengee kinachoendelea inatumika','A page cache plugin was not detected.'=>'Programu-jalizi ya akiba ya ukurasa haikutambuliwa.','A page cache plugin was detected.'=>'Programu-jalizi ya akiba ya ukurasa iligunduliwa.','There was %d client caching response header detected:'=>'Kulikuwa na %d ya kichwa cha majibu ya akiba ya mteja kilichotambuliwa:' . "\0" . 'Kulikuwa na vichwa %d vya majibu ya akiba ya mteja vimetambuliwa:','No client caching response headers were detected.'=>'Hakuna vichwa vya majibu vya akiba ya mteja vilivyotambuliwa.','Median server response time was %1$s milliseconds. It should be less than the recommended %2$s milliseconds threshold.'=>'Muda wa wastani wa kupata jibu kutoka seva ulikuwa milisekunde %1$s. Inapaswa kuwa chini ya kiwango kinachopendekezwa cha milisekunde %2$s.','Median server response time was %1$s milliseconds. This is less than the recommended %2$s milliseconds threshold.'=>'Muda wa wastani wa kupata jibu kutoka seva ulikuwa milisekunde %1$s. Hii ni chini ya kiwango kinachopendekezwa cha milisekunde %2$s.','Server response time could not be determined. Verify that loopback requests are working.'=>'Muda wa majibu ya seva haukuweza kubainishwa. Thibitisha kuwa maombi ya kurudi nyuma yanafanya kazi.','Page cache is detected but the server response time is still slow'=>'Akiba ya ukurasa imegunduliwa lakini muda wa majibu wa seva bado uko polepole','Page cache is not detected and the server response time is slow'=>'Akiba ya ukurasa haijatambuliwa na muda wa majibu wa seva uko polepole','Page cache is detected and the server response time is good'=>'Akiba ya ukurasa imegunduliwa na muda wa majibu wa seva ni mzuri','Page cache is not detected but the server response time is OK'=>'Akiba ya ukurasa haijatambuliwa lakini muda wa kujibu wa seva ni sawa','Unable to detect page cache due to possible loopback request problem. Please verify that the loopback request test is passing. Error: %1$s (Code: %2$s)'=>'Haijaweza kugundua akiba ya ukurasa kwa sababu ya tatizo linalowezekana la ombi la kurudi nyuma. Tafadhali thibitisha kuwa jaribio la ombi la kurudi nyuma linapita. Hitilafu: %1$s (Msimbo: %2$s)','Unable to detect the presence of page cache'=>'Haijaweza kutambua uwepo wa akiba ya ukurasa','Learn more about page cache'=>'Pata maelezo zaidi kuhusu akiba ya ukurasa','Page cache is detected by looking for an active page cache plugin as well as making three requests to the homepage and looking for one or more of the following HTTP client caching response headers:'=>'Akiba ya ukurasa hugunduliwa kwa kutafuta programu-jalizi ya akiba ya ukurasa inayotumika pamoja na kufanya maombi matatu kwa ukurasa wa nyumbani na kutafuta kichwa kimoja au zaidi cha majibu ya kache ya mteja wa HTTP:','Page cache enhances the speed and performance of your site by saving and serving static pages instead of calling for a page every time a user visits.'=>'Akiba ya ukurasa huongeza kasi na utendaji wa tovuti yako kwa kuhifadhi na kuhudumia kurasa tuli badala ya kuita ukurasa kila mtumiaji anapotembelea.','If you are still seeing this warning after having tried the actions below, you may need to contact your hosting provider for further assistance.'=>'Ikiwa bado unaona onyo hili baada ya kujaribu vitendo vilivyo hapa chini, unaweza kuhitaji kuwasiliana na mtoa huduma wako wa kukupangisha kwa usaidizi zaidi.','The Authorization header is used by third-party applications you have approved for this site. Without this header, those apps cannot connect to your site.'=>'Kijajuu cha Uidhinishaji kinatumiwa na maombi ya wahusika wengine ambao umeidhinisha kwa tovuti hii. Bila kichwa hiki, programu hizo haziwezi kuunganisha kwenye tovuti yako.','When testing the REST API, an unexpected result was returned:'=>'Wakati wa kujaribu API ya REST, matokeo yasiyotarajiwa yamerejeshwa:','REST API Response: (%1$s) %2$s'=>'Jibu la API REST: (%1$s) %2$s','REST API Endpoint: %s'=>'Endpoint ya API ya REST: %s','When testing the REST API, an error was encountered:'=>'Wakati wa kujaribu API ya REST, hitilafu ilipatikana:','Your site is running on an outdated version of PHP (%s), which does not receive security updates. It should be updated.'=>'Tovuti yako inaendeshwa kwa toleo la zamani la PHP (%s), ambalo halipokei masasisho ya usalama. Inapaswa kusasishwa.','Your site is running on an outdated version of PHP (%s), which does not receive security updates and soon will not be supported by WordPress.'=>'Tovuti yako inaendeshwa kwa toleo la zamani la PHP (%s), ambalo halipokei masasisho ya usalama na hivi karibuni halitaauniwa na WordPress.','Requirements'=>'Mahitaji','Your site is running on an outdated version of PHP (%s), which soon will not be supported by WordPress.'=>'Tovuti yako inatumia mfumo wa PHP (%s) uliopitwa na wakati, karibuni haitakubalika na WordPress','Your site does not have any installed themes.'=>'Tovuti yako haina mandhari yoyote iliyosakinishwa.','Your site does not have any active plugins.'=>'Tovuti yako haina programu jalizi zozote zinazotumika.','Another attempt will be made with the next release.'=>'Jaribio lingine litafanywa na toleo linalofuata.','The %1$s constant is defined as %2$s'=>'%1$s isiyobadilika inafafanuliwa kama %2$s','The %1$s argument must be a non-empty string for %2$s.'=>'Hoja ya %1$s lazima iwe mfuatano usio tupu wa %2$s.','The %s argument must be an array.'=>'Hoja ya %s lazima iwe safu.','- %1$s version %2$s%3$s'=>'- %1$s toleo %2$s%3$s','- %1$s (from version %2$s to %3$s)%4$s'=>'- %1$s (kutoka toleo %2$s hadi %3$s)%4$s','Reach out to WordPress Core developers to ensure you\'ll never have this problem again.'=>'Wasiliana na wasanidi wa WordPress Core ili kuhakikisha hutawahi kuwa na tatizo hili tena.','Important! Your version of WordPress (%1$s) will stop receiving security updates in the near future. To keep your site secure, please <a href="%2$s">update to the latest version of WordPress</a>.'=>'Muhimu! Toleo lako la WordPress (%1$s) litaacha kupokea masasisho ya usalama katika siku za usoni. Ili kuweka tovuti yako salama, tafadhali <a href="%2$s">sasisha hadi toleo jipya zaidi la WordPress</a>.','Important! Your version of WordPress (%1$s) is no longer supported, you will not receive any security updates for your website. To keep your site secure, please <a href="%2$s">update to the latest version of WordPress</a>.'=>'Muhimu! Toleo lako la WordPress (%1$s) halitumiki tena, hutapokea masasisho yoyote ya usalama kwa tovuti yako. Ili kuweka tovuti yako salama, tafadhali <a href="%2$s">sasisha hadi toleo jipya zaidi la WordPress</a>.','https://make.wordpress.org/core/wordpress-%s-field-guide/'=>'https://make.wordpress.org/core/wordpress-6-6-field-guide/','Learn more about WordPress %s'=>'Jifunze zaidi kuhusu WordPress %s','Please type your comment text.'=>'Tafadhali andika maoni yako.','You cannot remove users.'=>'Huwezi kuondoa watumiaji.','Application passwords grant access to <a href="%1$s">the %2$s site on the network as you have Super Admin rights</a>.'=>'Manenosiri ya programu huruhusu ufikiaji kwa <a href="%1$s">tovuti ya %2$s kwenye mtandao kwa kuwa una haki za Msimamizi Mkuu</a>.' . "\0" . 'Manenosiri ya programu huruhusu ufikiaji kwa <a href="%1$s">tovuti zote %2$s kwenye mtandao kwa kuwa una haki za Msimamizi Mkuu</a>.','WordPress has been updated! Next and final step is to update your database to the newest version.'=>'WordPress imesasishwa! Hatua inayofuata na ya mwisho ni kusasisha hifadhidata yako hadi toleo jipya zaidi.','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/appearance-themes-screen/">Documentation on Managing Themes</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/appearance-themes-screen/">Hati kuhusu Kusimamia Mandhari</a>','This information is being used to create a %s file.'=>'Maelezo haya yanatumiwa kuunda faili %s.','Welcome to WordPress. Before getting started, you will need to know the following items.'=>'Karibu kwenye WordPress. Kabla ya kuanza, utahitaji kujua vitu vifuatavyo.','Settings save failed.'=>'Mipangilio imeshindwa.','After your Privacy Policy page is set, you should edit it.'=>'Baada ya ukurasa wako wa Sera ya Faragha kuwekwa, unapaswa kuihariri.','<strong>Error:</strong> Your %1$s file is not <a href="%2$s">writable</a>, so updating it automatically was not possible. These are the mod_rewrite rules you should have in your %1$s file. Click in the field and press %3$s (or %4$s on Mac) to select all.'=>'<strong>Hitilafu:</strong> Faili yako ya %1$s <a href="%2$s">haiandikiki</a>, kwa hivyo haikuwezekana kuisasisha kiotomatiki. Hizi ndizo kanuni za mod_rewrite unazopaswa kuwa nazo katika faili yako ya %1$s. Bofya kwenye sehemu na ubonyeze %3$s (au %4$s kwenye Mac) ili kuchagua zote.','<strong>Error:</strong> Your %1$s file is not <a href="%2$s">writable</a>, so updating it automatically was not possible. This is the URL rewrite rule you should have in your %1$s file. Click in the field and press %3$s (or %4$s on Mac) to select all. Then insert this rule inside of the %5$s element in %1$s file.'=>'<strong>Hitilafu:</strong> Faili yako ya %1$s <a href="%2$s">haiandikiki</a>, kwa hivyo haikuwezekana kuisasisha kiotomatiki. Hii ndiyo sheria ya kuandika upya URL unayopaswa kuwa nayo katika faili yako ya %1$s. Bofya kwenye sehemu na ubonyeze %3$s (au %4$s kwenye Mac) ili kuchagua zote. Kisha ingiza sheria hii ndani ya kipengele cha %5$s katika faili %1$s.','An avatar is an image that can be associated with a user across multiple websites. In this area, you can choose to display avatars of users who interact with the site.'=>'Ishara ni picha inayoweza kuhusishwa na mtumiaji kwenye tovuti nyingi. Katika eneo hili, unaweza kuchagua kuonyesha ishara za watumiaji wanaoingiliana na tovuti.','Change Permalink Structure'=>'Badilisha Muundo wa Kiungo','Where your data is sent'=>'Ambapo data yako inatumwa','Copy &#8220;%s&#8221; URL to clipboard'=>'Nakili &#8220;%s&#8221; URL kwenye ubao wa kunakili','Some data that describes the error your site encountered has been put together.'=>'Baadhi ya data inayoelezea hitilafu iliyokumba tovuti yako imeunganishwa.','An attempt was made, but your site could not be updated automatically.'=>'Jaribio lilifanywa, lakini tovuti yako haikuweza kusasishwa kiotomatiki.','The update cannot be installed because some files could not be copied. This is usually due to inconsistent file permissions.'=>'Sasisho haliwezi kusakinishwa kwa sababu baadhi ya faili hazikuweza kunakiliwa. Kwa kawaida hii ni kutokana na ruhusa zisizolingana za faili.','<strong>Media</strong> &mdash; A list of URLs for media files the user uploads.'=>'<strong>Vyombo vya habari</strong> &mdash; Orodha ya URL za faili za midia ambazo mtumiaji anapakia.','<strong>Community Events Location</strong> &mdash; The IP Address of the user, which populates the Upcoming Community Events dashboard widget with relevant information.'=>'<strong>Eneo la Matukio ya Jumuiya</strong> &mdash; Anwani ya IP ya mtumiaji, ambayo hujaza wijeti ya dashibodi ya Matukio ya Jumuiya yajayo yenye taarifa muhimu.','WordPress collects (but <em>never</em> publishes) a limited amount of data from registered users who have logged in to the site. Generally, these users are people who contribute to the site in some way -- content, store management, and so on. With rare exceptions, these users do not include occasional visitors who might have registered to comment on articles or buy products. The data WordPress retains can include:'=>'WordPress hukusanya (lakini <em>haiwahi</em> kuchapisha) kiasi kidogo cha data kutoka kwa watumiaji waliojiandikisha ambao wameingia kwenye tovuti. Kwa ujumla, watumiaji hawa ni watu wanaochangia tovuti kwa namna fulani -- maudhui, usimamizi wa duka, na kadhalika. Isipokuwa nadra, watumiaji hawa hawajumuishi wageni wa mara kwa mara ambao wanaweza kuwa wamejiandikisha kutoa maoni kwenye makala au kununua bidhaa. Data iliyohifadhiwa na WordPress inaweza kujumuisha:','Note: Since this tool only gathers data from WordPress and participating plugins, you may need to do more to comply with export requests. For example, you should also send the requester some of the data collected from or stored with the 3rd party services your organization uses.'=>'Kumbuka: Kwa kuwa zana hii inakusanya data kutoka kwa WordPress na programu-jalizi zinazoshiriki pekee, huenda ukahitaji kufanya zaidi ili kutii maombi ya kuhamisha. Kwa mfano, unapaswa pia kumtumia mwombaji baadhi ya data iliyokusanywa kutoka au kuhifadhiwa na huduma za watu wengine ambao shirika lako linatumia.','Privacy Laws around the world require businesses and online services to provide an export of some of the data they collect about an individual, and to deliver that export on request. The rights those laws enshrine are sometimes called the "Right of Data Portability". It allows individuals to obtain and reuse their personal data for their own purposes across different services. It allows them to move, copy or transfer personal data easily from one IT environment to another.'=>'Sheria za Faragha duniani kote zinahitaji biashara na huduma za mtandaoni kutoa usafirishaji wa baadhi ya data wanazokusanya kuhusu mtu binafsi, na kuwasilisha mauzo hayo kwa ombi. Haki zilizowekwa na sheria hizo wakati mwingine huitwa "Haki ya Kubebeka kwa Data". Huruhusu watu binafsi kupata na kutumia tena data zao za kibinafsi kwa madhumuni yao wenyewe katika huduma mbalimbali. Inawaruhusu kuhamisha, kunakili au kuhamisha data ya kibinafsi kwa urahisi kutoka kwa mazingira moja ya IT hadi nyingine.','<strong>Comments</strong> &mdash; WordPress does not delete comments. The software does anonymize (but, again, <em>never</em> publishes) the associated Email Address, IP Address, and User Agent (Browser/OS).'=>'<strong>Maoni</strong> &mdash; WordPress haifuti maoni. Programu haitambui (lakini, tena, <em>haichapishi kamwe) Anwani ya Barua Pepe inayohusika, Anwani ya IP, na Ajenti ya Mtumiaji (Kivinjari/OS).','WordPress collects (but <em>never</em> publishes) a limited amount of data from logged-in users but then deletes it or anonymizes it. That data can include:'=>'WordPress hukusanya (lakini <em>haiwahi</em> kuchapisha) kiasi kidogo cha data kutoka kwa watumiaji walioingia katika akaunti lakini kisha kuifuta au kuficha utambulisho wake. Data hiyo inaweza kujumuisha:','Note: As this tool only gathers data from WordPress and participating plugins, you may need to do more to comply with erasure requests. For example, you are also responsible for ensuring that data collected by or stored with the 3rd party services your organization uses gets deleted.'=>'Kumbuka: Zana hii inapokusanya data kutoka kwa WordPress na programu-jalizi zinazoshiriki pekee, huenda ukahitaji kufanya zaidi ili kutii maombi ya kufuta. Kwa mfano, una jukumu pia la kuhakikisha kuwa data iliyokusanywa au kuhifadhiwa kwa huduma za watu wengine shirika lako linatumia inafutwa.','Privacy Laws around the world require businesses and online services to delete, anonymize, or forget the data they collect about an individual. The rights those laws enshrine are sometimes called the "Right to be Forgotten".'=>'Sheria za Faragha duniani kote zinahitaji biashara na huduma za mtandaoni kufuta, kuficha utambulisho, au kusahau data wanayokusanya kuhusu mtu binafsi. Haki zilizowekwa na sheria hizo wakati mwingine huitwa "Haki ya Kusahaulika".','This screen is where you manage requests to erase personal data.'=>'Skrini hii ndipo simamia maombi ya kufuta data ya kibinafsi.','This post is being backed up in your browser, just in case.'=>'Chapisho hili linahifadhiwa nakala katika kivinjari chako, endapo tu.','This will grant access to <a href="%1$s">the %2$s site on the network as you have Super Admin rights</a>.'=>'Hii itatoa idhini ya kufikia <a href="%1$s">tovuti ya %2$s kwenye mtandao kwa kuwa una haki za Msimamizi Mkuu</a>.' . "\0" . 'Hii itatoa idhini ya kufikia <a href="%1$s">tovuti zote %2$s kwenye mtandao kwa kuwa una haki za Msimamizi Mkuu</a>.','Learn about block themes'=>'Jifunze kuhusu mada za bloku','There is a new kind of WordPress theme, called a block theme, that lets you build the site you&#8217;ve always wanted &#8212; with blocks and styles.'=>'Kuna aina mpya ya mandhari ya WordPress, inayoitwa mandhari ya bloku, ambayo inakuwezesha kujenga tovuti ambayo umekuwa ukitaka kila mara &#8212; na vitalu na mitindo.','Discover a new way to build your site.'=>'Gundua mbinu mpya ya kutengeza tovuti yako.','Tweak your site, or give it a whole new look! Get creative &#8212; how about a new color palette or font?'=>'Rekebisha tovuti yako, au uipe sura mpya kabisa! Pata ubunifu &#8212; nje ungependa kujua kuhusu palette mpya ya rangi au fonti?','Switch up your site&#8217;s look & feel with Styles'=>'Badili mwonekano na mwonekano wa tovuti yako ukitumia Mitindo','Open the Customizer'=>'Fungua Kiteja','Configure your site&#8217;s logo, header, menus, and more in the Customizer.'=>'Sanidi nembo ya tovuti yako, kichwa, menyu, na zaidi k