dy have to show.'=>'Skrini ya Faragha hukuruhusu kuunda ukurasa mpya wa sera ya faragha au uchague moja ambayo tayari unapaswa kuonyesha.','Individual posts may override these settings. Changes here will only be applied to new posts.'=>'Machapisho ya mtu binafsi yanaweza kubatilisha mipangilio hii. Mabadiliko hapa yatatumika kwa machapisho mapya pekee.','Menu item moved to the top'=>'Kipengee cha menyu kimehamishwa hadi juu','Menu item removed'=>'Kipengee cha menyu kimeondolewa','The Dashboard is the first place you will come to every time you log into your site. It is where you will find all your WordPress tools. If you need help, just click the &#8220;Help&#8221; tab above the screen title.'=>'Dashibodi ni mahali pa kwanza ambapo utakuja kila wakati unapoingia kwenye tovuti yako. Ni mahali ambapo utapata zana zako zote za WordPress. Ikiwa unahitaji usaidizi, bofya tu &#8220;Msaada&#8221; kichupo juu ya kichwa cha skrini.','Welcome to your WordPress Dashboard!'=>'Karibu kwenye dashibodi yako ya WordPress','The application ID must be a UUID.'=>'Kitambulisho cha programu lazima kiwe UUID.','Select location'=>'Chagua eneo','Visit plugin site for %s'=>'Tembelea tovuti ya programu-jalizi kwa %s','pluginCannot Activate'=>'Haiwezi Kuamilisha','Max connections number'=>'Nambari ya juu zaidi ya miunganisho','Max allowed packet size'=>'Saizi ya juu inayoruhusiwa ya pakiti','Your website appears to use Basic Authentication, which is not currently compatible with application passwords.'=>'Tovuti yako inaonekana kutumia Uthibitishaji Msingi, ambao kwa sasa hauoani na nywila za programu.','%1$s &#8220;%2$s&#8221;'=>'%1$s &#8220;%2$s&#8221;','Template Editing'=>'Uhariri wa Kiolezo','WordPress comes with some awesome, worldview-changing rights courtesy of its <a href="%s">license</a>, the GPL.'=>'WordPress inakuja na haki nzuri za kubadilisha mtazamo wa ulimwengu kwa hisani ya <a href="%s">leseni</a> yake, GPL.','Want to see your name in lights on this page?'=>'Je, ungependa kuon