'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/tools-export-personal-data-screen/">Documentation on Export Personal Data</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/tools-export-personal-data-screen/">Hati kuhusu Hamisha Data ya Kibinafsi</a>','Many plugins may collect or store personal data either in the WordPress database or remotely. Any Export Personal Data request should include data from plugins as well.'=>'Programu-jalizi nyingi zinaweza kukusanya au kuhifadhi data ya kibinafsi kwenye hifadhidata ya WordPress au kwa mbali. Ombi lolote la Hamisha Data ya Kibinafsi linapaswa kujumuisha data kutoka kwa programu-jalizi pia.','If you are not sure, check the plugin documentation or contact the plugin author to see if the plugin collects data and if it supports the Data Exporter tool. This information may be available in the <a href="%s">Privacy Policy Guide</a>.'=>'Ikiwa huna uhakika, angalia hati za programu-jalizi au uwasiliane na mtunzi programu-jalizi ili kuona kama programu-jalizi inakusanya data na ikiwa inatumia zana ya Kisafirishaji Data. Taarifa hii inaweza kupatikana katika <a href="%s">Mwongozo wa Sera ya Faragha</a>.','<strong>Comments</strong> &mdash; For user comments, Email Address, IP Address, User Agent (Browser/OS), Date/Time, Comment Content, and Content URL.'=>'<strong>Maoni</strong> &mdash; Kwa maoni ya watumiaji, Anwani ya Barua pepe, Anwani ya IP, Wakala wa Mtumiaji (Kivinjari/OS), Tarehe/Saa, Maudhui ya Maoni, na URL ya Maudhui.','This screen is where you manage requests for an export of personal data.'=>'Skrini hii ndipo unapodhibiti maombi ya usafirishaji wa data ya kibinafsi.','Site URLs could not be switched to HTTPS.'=>'URL za tovuti hazikuweza kubadilishwa hadi HTTPS.','Site URLs switched to HTTPS.'=>'URL za tovuti zimebadilishwa hadi HTTPS.','It looks like HTTPS is not supported for your website at this point.'=>'Inaonekana HTTPS haitumiki kwa tovuti yako kwa wakati huu.','Sorry, you are not allowed to update this site to HTTPS.'=>'Samahani, huruhusiwi kusasisha tovuti hii hadi HTTPS.','Password reset links sent to %s user.'=>'Viungo vya kuweka upya nenosiri vimetumwa kwa mtumiaji %s.' . "\0" . 'Viungo vya kuweka upya nenosiri vimetumwa kwa watumiaji %s.','Password reset link sent.'=>'Kiungo cha kuweka upya nenosiri kimetumwa.','Send %s a link to reset their password. This will not change their password, nor will it force a change.'=>'Mtumie %s kiungo ili kuweka upya nenosiri lake. Hii haitabadilisha nenosiri lao, wala haitalazimisha mabadiliko.','Send Reset Link'=>'Tuma Kiungo cha Kuweka Upya','Policies'=>'Sera','The Privacy Settings require JavaScript.'=>'Mipangilio ya Faragha inahitaji JavaScript.','Privacy SettingsPolicy Guide'=>'Mwongozo wa Sera','Privacy SettingsSettings'=>'Mipangilio','Re-install version %s'=>'Sakinisha upya toleo la %s','Update to latest %s nightly'=>'Sasisha hadi %s mpya kila usiku','Send personal data erasure confirmation email.'=>'Tuma barua pepe ya uthibitishaji wa kufuta data ya kibinafsi.','Confirmation email'=>'Barua Pepe ya kuthibitisha','This tool helps site owners comply with local laws and regulations by deleting or anonymizing known data for a given user.'=>'Zana hii huwasaidia wamiliki wa tovuti kutii sheria na kanuni za eneo lako kwa kufuta au kuficha utambulisho wa data inayojulikana kwa mtumiaji fulani.','<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/tools-erase-personal-data-screen/">Documentation on Erase Personal Data</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/tools-erase-personal-data-screen/">Hati za Kufuta Data ya Kibinafsi</a>','Many plugins may collect or store personal data either in the WordPress database or remotely. Any Erase Personal Data request should delete data from plugins as well.'=>'Programu-jalizi nyingi zinaweza kukusanya au kuhifadhi data ya kibinafsi kwenye hifadhidata ya WordPress au kwa mbali. Ombi lolote la Kufuta Data ya Kibinafsi linapaswa kufuta data kutoka kwa programu-jalizi pia.','Plugin Data'=>'Data ya programu-jalizi','If you are not sure, check the plugin documentation or contact the plugin author to see if the plugin collects data and if it supports the Data Eraser tool. This information may be available in the <a href="%s">Privacy Policy Guide</a>.'=>'Ikiwa huna uhakika, angalia hati za programu-jalizi au uwasiliane na mtunzi programu-jalizi ili kuona kama programu-jalizi inakusanya data na ikiwa inaauni zana ya Kifuta Data. Taarifa hii inaweza kupatikana katika <a href="%s">Mwongozo wa Sera ya Faragha</a>.','<strong>Media</strong> &mdash; A list of URLs for all media file uploads made by the user.'=>'<strong>Vyombo vya habari</strong> &mdash; Orodha ya URL za upakiaji wa faili zote za media zilizofanywa na mtumiaji.','<strong>Session Tokens</strong> &mdash; User login information, IP Addresses, Expiration Date, User Agent (Browser/OS), and Last Login.'=>'<strong>Ishara za Kipindi</strong> &mdash; Maelezo ya kuingia kwa mtumiaji, Anwani za IP, Tarehe ya Mwisho wa Muda, Wakala wa Mtumiaji (Kivinjari/OS), na Kuingia Mara ya Mwisho.','<strong>Community Events Location</strong> &mdash; The IP Address of the user which is used for the Upcoming Community Events shown in the dashboard widget.'=>'<strong>Eneo la Matukio ya Jumuiya</strong> &mdash; Anwani ya IP ya mtumiaji ambayo inatumika kwa Matukio ya Jumuiya Yajayo inayoonyeshwa kwenye wijeti ya dashibodi.','<strong>Profile Information</strong> &mdash; user email address, username, display name, nickname, first name, last name, description/bio, and registration date.'=>'<strong>Maelezo ya Wasifu</strong> &mdash; anwani ya barua pepe ya mtumiaji, jina la mtumiaji, jina la kuonyesha, jina la utani, jina la kwanza, jina la mwisho, maelezo/wasifu, na tarehe ya usajili.','Default Data'=>'Data Chaguomsingi','The tool associates data stored in WordPress with a supplied email address, including profile data and comments.'=>'Chombo hiki huhusisha data iliyohifadhiwa katika WordPress na anwani y