s may not work as intended.'=>'Tukio lilolopangwa, %s, lilishindwa kuanza. Tovuti yako bado inafanya kazi, lakini hii inaweza kuonyesha kuwa kuchapisha machapisho au sasisho za kiotomatiki yainaweza kuwa haifanyi kazi kama ilivyokusudiwa.','A scheduled event has failed'=>'Tukio lililopangwa limeshindwa','While trying to test your site&#8217;s scheduled events, the following error was returned: %s'=>'Wakati wa kujaribu kujaribu matukio ya tovuti yako, makosa yafuatayo yalipatikana: %s','It was not possible to check your scheduled events'=>'Haikuwezekana kucheki matukio yako yaliyopangwa','Scheduled events are what periodically looks for updates to plugins, themes and WordPress itself. It is also what makes sure scheduled posts are published on time. It may also be used by various plugins to make sure that planned actions are executed.'=>'Matukio yaliyopangwa ndio yale huangalia sasisho kwa vijalizi, mionekano na WordPress yenyewe. Pia ndio yale yanayohakikisha machapisho yaliyopangwa yanachapishwa kwa wakati. Yanaweza pia kutumiwa na vijalizi mbalimbali kuhakikisha kuwa matendo yaliyopangwa yanafanywa.','Scheduled events are running'=>'Matukio yaliyopangwa yanaendelea','Talk to your web host about OpenSSL support for PHP.'=>'Ongea na host wako wa wavuti kuhusu msaada wa OpenSSL kwa PHP.','Your site is unable to communicate securely with other services'=>'Tovuti yako haiwezi kuwasiliana salama na huduma zingine','Your site can communicate securely with other services'=>'Tovuti yako haiwezi kuwasiliana salama na huduma zingine','Securely communicating between servers are needed for transactions such as fetching files, conducting sales on store sites, and much more.'=>'Kuwasiliana kwa usalama kati ya seva inahitajika kwa shughuli kama vile kupakua faili, kuendesha mauzo kwenye tovuti za kuuza kwenye tovuti za magala, na mengi zaidi.','Learn more about why you should use HTTPS'=>'Soma zaidi kuhusu mbona unafaa kutumia HTTPS','Your website does not use HTTPS'=>'Tovuti yak