ed %d character of <strong>unexpected output</strong> during activation.'=>'Kijalizi kilizalisha %d nukta ya <strong> matokeo yasiyotarajiwa </strong> wakati wa uwezeshaji.' . "\0" . 'Kijalizi kilizalisha %d nukta za <strong> matokeo yasiyotarajiwa </strong> wakati wa uwezeshaji.','Sorry, you are not allowed to resume this plugin.'=>'Samahani, hauruhusiwi kurejelea tena kijalizi hiki.','<strong>WordPress Events and News</strong> &mdash; Upcoming events near you as well as the latest news from the official WordPress project and the <a href="%s">WordPress Planet</a>.'=>'<strong> Matukio ya WordPress na Habari </strong>&mdash; Matukio yanayokuja karibu na wewe na vile vile habari mpya kutoka kwa mradi rasmi wa WordPress na <a href="%s"> Sayari ya WordPress </a>.','You cannot update because <a href="%1$s">WordPress %2$s</a> requires MySQL version %3$s or higher. You are running version %4$s.'=>'Hauwezi kusasisha kwa sababu <a href="%1$s"> WordPress %2$s</a> inahitaji toleo la MySQL %3$s au ya juu. Unatumia toleo %4$s.','You cannot update because <a href="%1$s">WordPress %2$s</a> requires PHP version %3$s or higher. You are running version %4$s.'=>'Hauwezi kusasisha kwa sababu <a href="%1$s"> WordPress %2$s</a> inahitaji toleo la PHP %3$s au la juu zaidi. Unatumia toleo %4$s.','Add menu items'=>'Ongeza vipengee vya menyu','or <a href="%s">create a new menu</a>. Do not forget to save your changes!'=>'au <a href="%s">unda menyu mpya</a>. Usikose kuhifadhi mabadiliko yako!','Click the Save Menu button to save your changes.'=>'Bonyeza kitufe cha Hifadhi Menu ili kuhifadhi mabadiliko yako.','Edit your menu below, or <a href="%s">create a new menu</a>. Do not forget to save your changes!'=>'Hariri menyu yako hapo chini, au <a href="%s">unda menyu mpya</a>. Usikose kuhifadhi mabadiliko yako!','Fill in the Menu Name and click the Create Menu button to create your first menu.'=>'Jaza Jina la Menyu na ubonyeze kitufe cha Unda Menyu ili kuunda menyu yako ya kwanza.','Create your first menu below.'=>'Unda menyu yako ya kwanza hapo chini.','You cannot install because <a href="%1$s">WordPress %2$s</a> requires MySQL version %3$s or higher. You are running version %4$s.'=>'Hauwezi kusasisha kwa sababu <a href="%1$s"> WordPress %2$s</a> inahitaji toleo la MySQL %3$s au la juu zaidi. Unatumia toleo %4$s.','You cannot install because <a href="%1$s">WordPress %2$s</a> requires PHP version %3$s or higher. You are running version %4$s.'=>'Hauwezi kusasisha kwa sababu <a href="%1$s"> WordPress %2$s</a> inahitaji toleo la PHP %3$s au ya juu zaidi. Unatumia toleo %4$s.','Learn more about updating PHP'=>'Jifunze zaidi kuhusu kusasisha PHP','What is PHP and how does it affect my site?'=>'PHP ni nini na inathirije tovuti yangu?','PHP Update Required'=>'Sasisho la PHP Lahitajika','You can find more details and make changes on the Plugins screen.'=>'Unaweza kupata maelezo zaidi na kufanya mabadiliko kwenye skrini ya Vijalizi.','One or more plugins failed to load properly.'=>'Kijalizi kimoja au zaidi limeshindwa kupika vizuri.','Could not resume the plugin.'=>'Haingeweza kurejelea kijalizi.','Custom PHP fatal error handler.'=>'Kidhibiti hitilafu kuu cha binafsi cha PHP.','Custom PHP error message.'=>'Ujumbe binafsi wa hitilafu ya PHP.','Could not remove the old translation.'=>'Haikuwezekana kuondoa tafsiri la kale.','Removing the old version of the translation&#8230;'=>'Inaondoa toleo la zamani la utafsiri&#8230;','<a href="%s" target="_parent">Click here to update WordPress</a>.'=>'<a href="%s" target="_parent">Bonyeza hapa kusasisha WordPress</a>.','<strong>Error:</strong> This plugin <strong>requires a newer version of WordPress</strong>.'=>'<strong>Hitilafu:</strong> Kijalizi hiki <strong>kinahitaji toleo jipya la WordPress</strong>.','<a href="%s" target="_blank">Click here to learn more about updating PHP</a>.'=>'<a href="%s" target="_blank">Bonyeza hapa ili kujua zaidi kuhusu kusasisha PHP</a>.','<strong>Error:</strong> This plugin <strong>requires a newer version of PHP</strong>.'=>'<strong>Hitilafu:</strong> Kijalizi hiki <strong>kinahitaji toleo jipya la PHP</strong>.','Add widget: %s'=>'Ongeza wijeti: %s','Add to: %s'=>'Ongeza kwa: %s','Track %s.'=>'Wimbo %s.','My Network'=>'Mtandao wangu','This plugin does not work with your version of PHP.'=>'Programu-jalizi hii haifanyi kazi na toleo lako la PHP.','This plugin does not work with your version of WordPress.'=>'Programu-jalizi hii haifanyi kazi na toleo lako la WordPress.','This plugin does not work with your versions of WordPress and PHP.'=>'Programu-jalizi hii haifanyi kazi na matoleo yako ya WordPress na PHP.','https://wordpress.org/documentation/wordpress-version/version-%s/'=>'https://wordpress.org/support/wordpress-version/version-%s/','Resume'=>'Endelea','pluginResume %s'=>'Endelea %s','You can find more details and make changes on the Themes screen.'=>'Unaweza kupata maelezo zaidi na kufanya mabadiliko kwenye skrini ya Mionekano.','One or more themes failed to load properly.'=>'Mwonekano mmoja au zaidi umeshindwa kupakia vizuri.','Could not resume the theme.'=>'Haingeweza kurejelea mwonekano.','Deleting a category does not delete the posts in that category. Instead, posts that were only assigned to the deleted category are set to the default category %s. The default category cannot be deleted.'=>'Kufuta kikundi haifuta machapisho kwenye kundi hilo. Badala yake, machapisho ambayo yalitumwa tu kwa kundi lililofutwa huwekwa kwenye kundi la msingi %s. Kundi la msingi haliwezi kufutwa.','The block widgets require JavaScript. Please enable JavaScript in your browser settings, or install the <a href="%s">Classic Widgets plugin</a>.'=>'Kihariri bloku kinahitaji JavaScript. Tafadhalu wezesha JavaScript katika mipangilio yako ya kibinafsi, au jaribu try <a href="%s">Kijalizi cha Classic Widgets</a>.','A post type mismatch has been detected.'=>'Kutofautiana kwa machapisho kumetambulika.','A post ID mismatch has been detected.'=>'Kutofautiana kwa vitambulisho vya 