=>'Tovuti lako %1$s imekumbana na hitilafu kubwa ikijaribu kusasisha kuwa toleo jipya la WordPress, %2$s.','WordPress %s is also now available.'=>'WordPress %s pia linapatikana sasa.','The update cannot be installed because your site is unable to copy some files. This is usually due to inconsistent file permissions.'=>'Sasisho haliwezi kusanikishwa kwa sababu hatutaweza kunakili faili kadhaa. Hii kawaida ni kwa sababu ya idhini zisizo sawa za faili.','Your translations are all up to date.'=>'Tafsiri zako zote ni asiria.','Translations'=>'Tafsiri','Error code: %s'=>'Kodi ya hitilafu: %s','Your hosting company, support forum volunteers, or a friendly developer may be able to use this information to help you:'=>'Your hosting company, support forum volunteers, or a friendly developer may be able to use this information to help you:','The WordPress Team'=>'Timu ya WordPress','You also have some plugins or themes with updates available. Update them now:'=>'Pia unazo vidude au dhima ambazo zinaweza kusasishwa. Zisasishe sasa:','If you experience any issues or need support, the volunteers in the WordPress.org support forums may be able to help.'=>'Ukikumbana na shida zozote ama ukiwa unataka usaidizi, kunao waliojitolea kwenye jukwaa za usaidizi ya WordPress wenye uwezo wa kukusaidia.','Keeping your site updated is important for security. It also makes the internet a safer place for you and your readers.'=>'Usasisho wa tovuti lako ni muhimu kwa usalama. Pia inachangia kuifanya mtandao kuwa salama kwako na kwa wasomaji wako.','Please check out your site now. It\'s possible that everything is working. If it says you need to update, you should do so:'=>'Tafadhali, tembelea tovuti lako sasa. Kuna uwezekano kuwa kila kitu kiko shwari. Ukipata kwamba usasisho linahitajika, unastahili kufanya hivyo:','This means your site may be offline or broken. Don\'t panic; this can be fixed.'=>'Hii inamaanisha tovuti lako haliko mtandaoni ama limevunjika. Usiwe na hofu; hili linaweza kurekebishwa.','Your site at %1$s experienced a critical failure while trying to update to the latest version of WordPress, %2$s.'=>'Tovuti lako %1$s limekumbana na hitilafu kubwa ikijaribu kusasisha kuwa toleo jipya la WordPress, %2$s.','Updating is easy and only takes a few moments:'=>'Usasisho ni rahisi na utachukua muda mfupi:','Please update your site at %1$s to WordPress %2$s.'=>'Tafadhali, sasisha tovuti lako kwa %1$s hadi WordPress %2$s.','For more on version %s, see the About WordPress screen:'=>'Kujua zaidi kuhusu toleo %s, angalia skrini Kuhusu WordPress:','No further action is needed on your part.'=>'Hakuna unachohitajiwa kufanya tena.','Howdy! Your site at %1$s has been updated automatically to WordPress %2$s.'=>'Jambo! Tovuti lako %1$s limesasishwa kiotomatiki kuwa WordPress%2$s .','[%1$s] URGENT: Your site may be down due to a failed update'=>'[%1$s] DHARURA: Tovuti lako linaweza kuwa na changamoto kutokana na usasisho uliofeli.','[%1$s] WordPress %2$s is available. Please update!'=>'[%1$s] WordPress %2$s linapatikana. Tafadhali sasisha!','[%1$s] Your site has updated to WordPress %2$s'=>'[%1$s] Tovuti lako limesasishwa kuwa %2$s','Translations for %s'=>'Tafsiri ya %s','Updating translations for %1$s (%2$s)&#8230;'=>'Sasisho la tafsiri za %1$s (%2$s)&#8230;','Update Translations'=>'Sasisha tafsiri','Background updates'=>'Background updates','There is not enough free disk space to complete the update.'=>'Hakuna nafasi cha kutosha kwenye diski ili kusasisha.','Updating plugin: %s'=>'Kidude kinasasishwa: %s','Updating theme: %s'=>'Dhima linasasishwa: %s','Translation updated successfully.'=>'Sasisho la tafsiri imekamilika vilivyo.','Translation update failed.'=>'Usasisho wa tafsiri umefeli.','Some of your translations need updating. Sit tight for a few more seconds while they are updated as well.'=>'Tafsiri zako zingine zinahitaji kusasishwa. Ngoja kidogo tukizisasisha pia.','Create a brand new user and add them to this site.'=>'Huluku watumiaji wengine wapia na uwaongeze kwenye tovuti hili.','Upgrading to a newer version of the same theme will override changes made here. To avoid this, consider creating a <a href="%s">child theme</a> instead.'=>'Kusasisha kuwa toleo mpya la dhima hilo hilo litafuta mabadiliko yaliyofanywa hapa. Kuzuia hii, fikiria kuhuluku <a href="%s">dhima ndogo </a> badala yake.','The sizes listed below determine the maximum dimensions in pixels to use when adding an image to the Media Library.'=>'Viwango vilivyoorodheshwa hapa chini litahakiki vipimo vikubwa zaidi kwa pikseli za kutumia kwenye kuongeza picha kwenye Maktaba ya Midia.','Comment must be manually approved'=>'Chapisho ni lazima iidhinishwe binafsi.','<strong>Clicking the arrow to the right of any menu item</strong> in the editor will reveal a standard group of settings. Additional settings such as link target, CSS classes, link relationships, and link descriptions can be enabled and disabled via the Screen Options tab.'=>'<strong>Clicking the arrow to the right of any menu item</strong> in the editor will reveal a standard group of settings. Additional settings such as link target, CSS classes, link relationships, and link descriptions can be enabled and disabled via the Screen Options tab.','Menus can be displayed in locations defined by your theme, even used in sidebars by adding a &#8220;Navigation Menu&#8221; widget on the <a href="%1$s">Widgets</a> screen. If your theme does not support the navigation menus feature (the default themes, %2$s and %3$s, do), you can learn about adding this support by following the documentation link to the side.'=>'Menyu zinaweza kuonyeshwa katika maeneo yaliyofafanuliwa na mandhari yako, hata kutumika katika upau wa pembeni kwa kuongeza &#8220;Menyu ya Urambazaji&#8221; wijeti kwenye skrini ya <a href="%1$s">Wijeti</a>. Ikiwa mandhari yako hayaauni kipengele cha menyu za kusogeza (mandhari chaguo-msingi, %2$s na %3$s, je), unaweza kupata maelezo kuhusu kuongeza usaidizi huu kwa kufuata kiungo cha uhifadhi kando.','Your theme does not natively support menus, but you can use them in sidebars by adding a &#8220;Navigation Menu&#8221; widget on the <a href="%s">Widgets</a> screen.'=>'Your theme does not natively support menus, but you can use them in sidebars by adding a &#8220;Navigation Menu&#8221; widget on the <a href="%s">Widgets</a> screen.','Sorry, that is not a valid email address. Email addresses look like <code>username@example.com</code>.'=>'Samahani, hii sio anwani ya barua pepe inayokubalika. Anwani ya barua pepe inafanana hivi <code>username@example.com</code>','You must provide an email address.'=>'Lazima utoe anwani yako ya barua pepe.','Your passwords do not match. Please try again.'=>'Nywila zako haviambatani. Tafadhali jaribu tena.','The username you provided has invalid characters.'=>'Jina la utumizi uliopeana ina vibambo visivyokubalika.','Please provide a valid username.'=>'Tafadhali peana jina la mtumizi sawa.','Copying the required files&#8230;'=>'Kunakili faili zinazohitajika&#8230;','Preparing to install the latest version&#8230;'=>'Inajiandaa kusanikisha toleo la kisasa&#8230;','This password will not be stored on the server.'=>'This password will not be stored on the server.','The checksum of the file (%1$s) does not match the expected checksum value (%2$s).'=>'The checksum of the file (%1$s) does not match the expected checksum value (%2$s).','WordPress %s'=>'WordPress %s','Updating to WordPress %s'=>'Inasasisha kuwa WordPress %s','Due to an error during updating, WordPress has been restored to your previous version.'=>'Kutokana na kosa lilitokea wakati wa kusasisha, WordPress imerudi kwa toleo ya awali.','Looking for %1$s in %2$s'=>'Inatafuta %1$s kwa %2$s','%s page restored from the Trash.'=>'%s ukurasa imerejeshwa kutoka kwa taka' . "\0" . '%s kurasa zimerejeshwa kutoka kwa taka','%s page moved to the Trash.'=>'%s ukurasa umehamishwa kwa taka.' . "\0" . '%s Kurasa zimehamishwa kwa taka','%s page permanently deleted.'=>'%s ukurasa umefutwa kikamilifu.' . "\0" . '%s kurasa imefutwa kikamilifu.','%s page not updated, somebody is editing it.'=>'%s ukurasa haujasasishwa, kuna anayeihariri.' . "\0" . '%s kurasa hazijasasishwa, kuna anayezihariri.','%s page updated.'=>'%s ukurasa umesasishwa.' . "\0" . '%s ukurasa zimesasishwa.','%s post restored from the Trash.'=>'%s chapisho imerejeshwa kutoka kwa taka.' . "\0" . '%s machapisho yamerejeshwa kutoka kwa taka.','%s post moved to the Trash.'=>'%s chapisho imehamishwa kwa taka.' . "\0" . '%s machapisho yamehamishwa kwenye taka.','%s post permanently deleted.'=>'%s chapisho imefutwa kikamilifu.' . "\0" . '%s machapisho yamefutwa kikamilifu.','%s post not updated, somebody is editing it.'=>'%s chapisho halijasasishwa, kuna anayeihariri.' . "\0" . '%s machapisho hayajasasishwa, kuna anayezihariri.','Tags deleted.'=>'Lebo zimefutwa.','Tag not updated.'=>'Lebo halijasasishwa.','Tag not added.'=>'Lebo halijaongezwa.','Tag updated.'=>'Lebo limesasishwa.','Tag deleted.'=>'Lebo imefutwa.','Tag added.'=>'Lebo imeongezwa.','Categories deleted.'=>'Vikundi vimefutwa.','Category not updated.'=>'Kikundi hakijasasishwa.','Category not added.'=>'Kikundi hakijaongezwa.','Category updated.'=>'Kikundi kimesasishwa.','Category deleted.'=>'Kikundi kimefutwa.','Category added.'=>'Kikundi kimeongezwa.','Compare two different revisions by <strong>selecting the &#8220;Compare any two revisions&#8221; box</strong> to the side.'=>'Linganisha marekebisho mawili tofauti na <strong> kuchagua kisanduku cha &#8220;Linganisha marekebisho yoyote mawili&#8221; </strong> kwa upande.','Compare any two revisions'=>'Linganisha marudio yoyote mbili.','Restore This Autosave'=>'Rejesha rekebisho hii','Current Revision by %s'=>'Rudio la Sasa na %s','Autosave by %s'=>'Hifadhi kiotomatiki na %s','revisionsBrowse'=>'Vinjari','Revisions: %s'=>'Marudio: %s','"%s".'=>'"%s".','"%1$s" by %2$s.'=>'"%1$s" kwa %2$s.','"%1$s" from %2$s.'=>'"%1$s" kutoka %2$s.','"%1$s" from %2$s by %3$s.'=>'"%1$s" kutoka %2$s kwa %3$s.','Revision by %s'=>'Rekebisho na %s','<strong>Connection lost.</strong> Saving has been disabled until you are reconnected.'=>'<strong>Muunganisho umepotea.</strong> Kuhifadhi kumezimwa hadi utakapounganishwa tena.','Repeat Password'=>'Rudia nywila','Repeat New Password'=>'Rudia nywila mpya','Add menu items from the column on the left.'=>'Ongeza vipengee vya menu kutoka kwa safuwima ilioko kushoto','http://wordpress.org/plugins/hello-dolly/'=>'http://wordpress.org/plugins/hello-dolly/','The theme contains no files.'=>'Dhima haina faili.','The package contains no files.'=>'Kifurushi hiki hakina faili.','To navigate between revisions, <strong>drag the slider handle left or right</strong> or <strong>use the Previous or Next buttons</strong>.'=>'Ili kurambaza kati ya marekebisho, <strong> vjuta slider kushoto au kulia </strong> au <strong> tumia vitufe vya Iliyotangulia au Ifuatavyo </strong>.','Loading&hellip;'=>'Inapakia&hellip;','This item has already been deleted.'=>'Kipengee hiki kimefutwa tayari.','The item you are trying to restore from the Trash no longer exists.'=>'Kipengee unachojaribu kurejesha kutoka kwa taka halipo sasa.','The item you are trying to move to the Trash no longer exists.'=>'Kipengee unachojaribu kuhamisha kwa taka halipo sasa.','Drag the items into the order you prefer. Click the arrow on the right of the item to reveal additional configuration options.'=>'Vuta kila kitu kwenye mpangilio unayopendelea. Bonyeza mshale upande wa kulia wa bidhaa kufunua chaguzi zaidi za usanidi.','If you have not yet created any menus, <strong>click the &#8217;create a new menu&#8217; link</strong> to get started'=>'Ikiwa haujatengeneza menyu yoyote, <strong> bonyeza kitufe cha &#8217;unda orodha mpya&#8217; </strong> ili kuanza','To restore a revision, <strong>click Restore This Revision</strong>.'=>'Kurejesa rekebisho, <strong>bofya Rejesha Hii Rekebisho</strong>.','From this screen you can review, compare, and restore revisions:'=>'Kutoka kwenye skrini hii unaweza kuhakikisha, kulinganisha na kurejesha marekebisho.','Revisions are saved copies of your post or page, which are periodically created as you update your content. The red text on the left shows the content that was removed. The green text on the right shows the content that was added.'=>'Marekebisho ni nakala zilizohifadhiwa za chapisho lako au ukurasa, ambazo huundwa kila wakati unasasisha yaliyomo yako. Nakala nyekundu upande wa kushoto inaonyesha yaliyomo ambayo iliondolewa. Nakala ya kijani upande wa kulia inaonyesha yaliyomo.','This screen is used for managing your content revisions.'=>'Skrini hii inatumika kudhibiti marekebisho ya maudhui.','Followed by post revision infoTo:'=>'Kwa:','Button label for a next revisionNext'=>'Ifuatayo','Button label for a previous revisionPrevious'=>'Iliopita','Followed by post revision infoFrom:'=>'Kutoka kwa:','menuUse new menu'=>'Tumia menyu mpya','menuEdit'=>'Hariri','Select a Menu'=>'Chagua menyu','Assigned Menu'=>'Menyu iliyotengwa','Theme Location'=>'Mahali pa dhima','Manage Locations'=>'Dhibiti Mahali','Edit Menus'=>'Hariri menyu','To add a new menu instead of assigning an existing one, <strong>click the &#8217;Use new menu&#8217; link</strong>. Your new menu will be automatically assigned to that theme location'=>'Ili kuongeza menyu mpya badala ya kugawa iliyopo, <strong>bonyeza kiungo cha &#8217;Tumia menyu mpya&#8217;</strong>. Menyu yako mpya itawekwa moja kwa moja eneo la mwonekano','To edit a menu currently assigned to a theme location, <strong>click the adjacent &#8217;Edit&#8217; link</strong>'=>'Ili kuhariri menyu iliyopewa eneo la mwonekano kwa sasa, <strong> bofya kiunga cha karibu cha &#8217;Hariri&#8217; </strong>','To assign menus to one or more theme locations, <strong>select a menu from each location&#8217;s dropdown</strong>. When you are finished, <strong>click Save Changes</strong>'=>'Ili kugawa menyu katika eneo la mandhari moja au zaidi, <strong> chagua menyu kutoka kwa kila eneo kushuka. </strong> Unapomaliza, <strong> bonyeza Hifadhi Mabadiliko </strong>','This screen is used for globally assigning menus to locations defined by your theme.'=>'Skrini hii inatumika kwa kuwapa menyu ulimwenguni kwa maeneo yaliyofafanuliwa na mwonekano wako.','Editing Menus'=>'Uhariri wa dhima','Delete a menu item by <strong>expanding it and clicking the Remove link</strong>'=>'Futa kipengee cha menyu kwa <strong> kupanua na kubonyeza kiunga cha Ondoa </strong>','To reorganize menu items, <strong>drag and drop items with your mouse or use your keyboard</strong>. Drag or move a menu item a little to the right to make it a submenu'=>'Ili kupanga upya vitu vya menyu, <strong> Vuta na ushushe vitu na panya yako au utumie kibodi yako </strong>. Buruta au uhamishe kitu cha menyu kidogo kulia ili kuifanya iwe ndogo','Add one or several items at once by <strong>selecting the checkbox next to each item and clicking Add to Menu</strong>'=>'Ongeza kitu kimoja au kadhaa mara moja kwa <strong> kuchagua kisanduku cha ukaguzi karibu na kila kitu na kubonyeza Ongeza kwenye Menyu </strong>','Each navigation menu may contain a mix of links to pages, categories, custom URLs or other content types. Menu links are added by selecting items from the expanding boxes in the left-hand column below.'=>'Kila menyu ya urambazaji inaweza kuwa na mchanganyiko wa kurasa, vikundi, URL maalum na aina zingine za yaliyomo. Viunga vya menyu huongezwa kwa kuchagua vitu kutoka kwa visanduku vya kupanua kwenye safu ya mkono wa kushoto chini.','Menu Management'=>'Udhibiti wa menyu','You can assign theme locations to individual menus by <strong>selecting the desired settings</strong> at the bottom of the menu editor. To assign menus to all theme locations at once, <strong>visit the Manage Locations tab</strong> at the top of the screen.'=>'Unaweza kugawa maeneo ya mwonekano kwa menyu ya kibinafsi kwa <strong> kuchagua mipangilio inayotaka </strong> chini ya hariri ya menyu. Ili kugawa menyu kwa maeneo yote ya mandhari mara moja, <strong> tembelea kichupo cha Usimamizi wa eneo </strong> juu ya skrini.','To edit an existing menu, <strong>choose a menu from the dropdown and click Select</strong>'=>'Ili kuhariri menyu iliyopo, <strong> chagua menyu kutoka kwa kushuka chini na ubonyeze Chagua </strong>','The menu management box at the top of the screen is used to control which menu is opened in the editor below.'=>'Kisanduku cha kidhibiti menyu iliyopo juu ya skrini linatumika kuthibiti menyu ambayo itafunguliwa kwenye kihariri iliyopo hapa chini.','Add, organize, and modify individual menu items'=>'Ongeza, panga, na urekebishe vitu vya menyu','Create, edit, and delete menus'=>'Huluku, hariri na futa menyu','From this screen you can:'=>'Kutoka kwenye skrini hii unaweza:','This screen is used for managing your navigation menus.'=>'Skrini hii inatumika katika kusimamia menyu yako ya urambazaji.','Menu locations updated.'=>'Mahali pa menyu pamesasishwa','Your latest changes were saved as a revision.'=>'Mabadiliko yako ya mwisho yamehifadhiwa kama rekebisho.','Audio Codec:'=>'Codec ya Sauti:','Audio Format:'=>'Fomati ya Sauti:','Genre: %s.'=>'Utanzu: %s.','Track %1$s of %2$s.'=>'Wimbo %1$s wa %2$s.','Released: %d.'=>'Ilitolewa: %d.','%1$s by %2$s.'=>'%1$s kwa %2$s.','Restore This Revision'=>'Rejesha rekebisho hii','Denied: %s'=>'Imekataliwa: %s','Capabilities'=>'Uwezo','Menu Settings'=>'Mipangilio ya menyu','Menu structure'=>'Muundo wa menyu','To the top'=>'Hadi juu','Down one'=>'Ya chini','Up one'=>'Ya juu','Move'=>'Hamisha','Draft created on %1$s at %2$s'=>'Mswadajaribio imehulukiwa mnamo %1$s wakati wa %2$s','You cannot move this item to the Trash. %s is currently editing.'=>'Huwezi kuhamisha kipengee hiki kwenye taka. %s linahariri','%s has taken over and is currently editing.'=>'%s amechukua usukani na sasa anahariri.','Select a menu to edit:'=>'Chagua menyu ya kuhariri:','Thank you for Updating! Please visit the <a href="%s">Upgrade Network</a> page to update all your sites.'=>'Asante kwa kusasisha! Tafadhali tembelea <a href="%s">Sasisha mtandao</a> ukurasa kusasisha tovuti zako zote.','All right, sparky! You&#8217;ve made it through this part of the installation. WordPress can now communicate with your database. If you are ready, time now to&hellip;'=>'Sawa sawa! Umetoboa sehemu hii ya usakinishaji. WordPress inaweza kuwasiliana na hifadhidata yako. Sasa uko tayari, ni wakati wa&hellip;','Client version'=>'Toleo la mteja','Auto add pages'=>'Iongeze kurasa yenyewe','Give your menu a name, then click Create Menu.'=>'Patia menyu lako jina, alafu bofya Huluku Menyu','Edit your default menu by adding or removing items. Drag the items into the order you prefer. Click Create Menu to save your changes.'=>'Hariri menyu yako chaguo-msingi kwa kuongeza au kuondoa vitu. Buruta kila kitu kwenye mpangilio unayopendelea. Bonyeza Unda Menyu kuokoa mabadiliko yako.','Selected menus have been successfully deleted.'=>'Menyu zilizochaguliwa zimefutwa','For PHP files, you can use the documentation dropdown to select from functions recognized in that file. Look Up takes you to a web page with reference material about that particular function.'=>'Kwa faili za PHP, unaweza kutumia kushuka kwa Hati kuchagua kutoka kwa kazi zinazotambuliwa kwenye faili hiyo. Angalia inakuchukua kwa ukurasa wa tovuti na nyenzo za kumbukumbu juu ya kazi hiyo.','Look Up'=>'Angalia juu','The documentation menu below the editor lists the PHP functions recognized in the plugin file. Clicking Look Up takes you to a web page about that particular function.'=>'Menyu ya nyaraka iliyo chini ya kihariri huorodhesha vitendaji vya PHP vinavyotambuliwa kwenye faili ya programu-jalizi. Kubofya Angalia Juu kunakupeleka kwenye ukurasa wa wavuti kuhusu kipengele hicho maalum.','%s is currently editing'=>'%s linahariri kwa wakati huu','You can upload and insert media (images, audio, documents, etc.) by clicking the Add Media button. You can select from the images and files already uploaded to the Media Library, or upload new media to add to your page or post. To create an image gallery, select the images to add and click the &#8220;Create a new gallery&#8221; button.'=>'You can upload and insert media (images, audio, documents, etc.) by clicking the Add Media button. You can select from the images and files already uploaded to the Media Library, or upload new media to add to your page or post. To create an image gallery, select the images to add and click the &#8220;Create a new gallery&#8221; button.','Image rotation is not supported by your web host.'=>'Mzunguko wa picha haujawezeshwa na mwenyeji wako wa tovuti.','If you are looking to use the link manager, please install the <a href="%s">Link Manager plugin</a>.'=>'Ikiwa unatazamia kutumia kidhibiti cha kiungo, tafadhali sakinisha <a href="%s">programu jalizi ya Kidhibiti cha Kiungo</a>.','When changing themes, there is often some variation in the number and setup of widget areas/sidebars and sometimes these conflicts make the transition a bit less smooth. If you changed themes and seem to be missing widgets, scroll down on this screen to the Inactive Widgets area, where all of your widgets and their settings will have been saved.'=>'Wakati wa kubadilisha mionekano, mara nyingi kuna utofauti katika idadi na usanidi wa maeneo / njia za widget na wakati mwingine mzozo huu hufanya ubadilishaji kuwa laini kidogo. Ikiwa ulibadilisha mada na unaonekana kuwa unakosa vilivyoandikwa, shuka chini kwenye skrini hii hadi eneo la Kikasha kisichotumika, ambapo vilivyoandikwa vyako vyote na mipangilio yake vitahifadhiwa.','<strong>Parent</strong> &mdash; Categories, unlike tags, can have a hierarchy. You might have a Jazz category, and under that have child categories for Bebop and Big Band. Totally optional. To create a subcategory, just choose another category from the Parent dropdown.'=>'<strong>Parent</strong> &mdash; Categories, unlike tags, can have a hierarchy. You might have a Jazz category, and under that have child categories for Bebop and Big Band. Totally optional. To create a subcategory, just choose another category from the Parent dropdown.','Several boxes on this screen contain settings for how your content will be published, including:'=>'Visanduku vingi kwenye skrini hii vina mpangilio kuonyesha jinsi ambavyo maudhui yako yatachapishwa','Inserting Media'=>'Kuingiza Midia','The title field and the big Post Editing Area are fixed in place, but you can reposition all the other boxes using drag and drop. You can also minimize or expand them by clicking the title bar of each box. Use the Screen Options tab to unhide more boxes (Excerpt, Send Trackbacks, Custom Fields, Discussion, Slug, Author) or to choose a 1- or 2-column layout for this screen.'=>'Sehemu ya kichwa na eneo Kubwa la Kuhariri zimewekwa mahali, lakini unaweza kuweka tena masanduku mengine yote kwa kutumia Kuvuta na Kushusha. Unaweza pia kuipunguza au kuipanua kwa kubonyeza upau wa kichwa kwenye kila sanduku. Tumia kichupo cha Chaguzi za Screen ili kuifuta sanduku zaidi (Kutoka, Tuma Vinjari, Sehemu za Forodha, Majadiliano, Slug, Mwandishi) au uchague mpangilio wa safu wima 1- au 2 ya skrini hii.','Do not forget to click &#8220;Save Changes&#8221; when you are done!'=>'Usisahau kubonyeza: Hifadhi Mabadiliko ukimaliza!','To use a background image, simply upload it or choose an image that has already been uploaded to your Media Library by clicking the &#8220;Choose Image&#8221; button. You can display a single instance of your image, or tile it to fill the screen. You can have your background fixed in place, so your site content moves on top of it, or you can have it scroll with your site.'=>'To use a background image, simply upload it or choose an image that has already been uploaded to your Media Library by clicking the &#8220;Choose Image&#8221; button. You can display a single instance of your image, or tile it to fill the screen. You can have your background fixed in place, so your site content moves on top of it, or you can have it scroll with your site.','media itemEdit'=>'Hariri','colorDefault: %s'=>'Cha msingi: %s','column nameUploaded to'=>'Imepakiwa Kwenda','The uploaded file is not a valid image. Please try again.'=>'The uploaded file is not a valid image. Please try again.','Choose a Custom Header'=>'Chagua kijajuu msingi','Choose a Background Image'=>'Chagua picha ya mandharinyuma','In the Header Text section of this page, you can choose whether to display this text or hide it. You can also choose a color for the text by clicking the Select Color button and either typing in a legitimate HTML hex value, e.g. &#8220;#ff0000&#8221; for red, or by choosing a color using the color picker.'=>'Katika Sehemu ya Maandishi ya Header ya ukurasa huu, unaweza kuchagua kuonyesha maandishi haya au kuificha. Unaweza pia kuchagua rangi kwa maandishi kwa kubonyeza kitufe cha Rangi Chagua na uchapishe kwa halali halali ya HTML hex, n.k. e.g. &#8220;#ff0000&#8221; kwa nyekundu, au kwa kuchagua rangi kwa kutumia kichaa rangi.','You can also choose a background color by clicking the Select Color button and either typing in a legitimate HTML hex value, e.g. &#8220;#ff0000&#8221; for red, or by choosing a color using the color picker.'=>'You can also choose a background color by clicking the Select Color button and either typing in a legitimate HTML hex value, e.g. &#8220;#ff0000&#8221; for red, or by choosing a color using the color picker.','In the <strong>In response to</strong> column, there are three elements. The text is the name of the post that inspired the comment, and links to the post editor for that entry. The View Post link leads to that post on your live site. The small bubble with the number in it shows the number of approved comments that post has received. If there are pending comments, a red notification circle with the number of pending comments is displayed. Clicking the notification circle will filter the comments screen to show only pending comments on that post.'=>'Katika <strong>kwa kujibu</strong> safuwima, kuna vipengele vitatu. Maandishi ni jina la chapisho ambalo lilihimiza maoni, na viungo vya kihariri cha chapisho kwa ingizo hilo. Kiungo cha Tazama Chapisho kinaongoza kwa chapisho hilo kwenye tovuti yako ya moja kwa moja. Kiputo kidogo kilicho na nambari ndani yake kinaonyesha idadi ya maoni yaliyoidhinishwa ambayo chapisho limepokea. Ikiwa kuna maoni ambayo hayajashughulikiwa, duara nyekundu ya arifa yenye idadi ya maoni yanayosubiri huonyeshwa. Kubofya mduara wa arifa kutachuja skrini ya maoni ili kuonyesha maoni yanayosubiri tu kwenye chapisho hilo.','ID #%1$s: %2$s'=>'ID #%1$s: %2$s','ID #%1$s: %2$s <strong>The current user will not be deleted.</strong>'=>'ID #%1$s: %2$s <strong>Mtumiaji wa sasa hatafutwa.</strong>','Used: %1$s%% of %2$s'=>'Linalotumika: %1$s%% of %2$s','Please select an option.'=>'Tafadhali chagua kitendo.','After you&#8217;ve done that, click &#8220;Run the installation&#8221;.'=>'Ukimalizana na hilo, bonyeza Anzisha usanukishaji;','If you want to install a plugin that you&#8217;ve downloaded elsewhere, click the Upload Plugin button above the plugins list. You will be prompted to upload the .zip package, and once uploaded, you can activate the new plugin.'=>'Ikiwa unataka kusanikisha kijalizi ambacho umeshapakua mahali pengine, bonyeza kitufe cha Kuweka Pakia juu ya orodha ya vijalizi. Utasababishwa kupakia kifurushi cha .zip, na mara moja ukipakia, unaweza kuamsha kijalizi kipya.','You can also browse a user&#8217;s favorite plugins, by using the Favorites link above the plugins list and entering their WordPress.org username.'=>'Pia unaweza kuvinjari vidude vipendwa vyamtumiaji kwa kutumia kiungo kipendwa juu ya orodha ya vidude na kuingiza jina lake la utumizi la WordPress.org','If you know what you are looking for, Search is your best bet. The Search screen has options to search the WordPress Plugin Directory for a particular Term, Author, or Tag. You can also search the directory by selecting popular tags. Tags in larger type mean more plugins have been labeled with that tag.'=>'Ikiwa unajua unachotafuta, Tafuta ni bet yako bora. Skrini ya Utafutaji ina chaguzi za kutafuta Saraka ya programu-jalizi ya WordPress kwa kipindi fulani, Mwandishi, au Tag. Unaweza pia kutafuta saraka kwa kuchagua vitambulisho maarufu. Tepe katika aina kubwa inamaanisha kuwa programu-jalizi zaidi zimepigwa alama na lebo hiyo.','It is up to search engines to honor this request.'=>'Ni jukumu la mashine taftishi kufuata agizo hili.','Discourage search engines from indexing this site'=>'Kataza injini za utafutaji kutoka kwa kuashiria tovuti hii','Allow search engines to index this site'=>'Ruhusu injini za utafutaji kuashiria tovuti hii. ','Search engine visibility'=>'Uonekano wa mashine taftishi','Welcome to WordPress %1$s. You will be redirected to the About WordPress screen. If not, click <a href="%2$s">here</a>.'=>'Karibu WordPress%1$s. Utaelekezwa kwa skrini ya Kuhusu WordPress. La sivyo, bonyeza <a href="%2$s">here</a>.','Get Favorites'=>'Pata vipendwa','Your WordPress.org username:'=>'Jina lako la utumizi kwenye WordPress.org','If you have marked plugins as favorites on WordPress.org, you can browse them here.'=>'If you have marked plugins as favorites on WordPress.org, you can browse them here.','Welcome to WordPress!'=>'Karibu WordPress!','Search engines discouraged'=>'Injini za Utafutaji zimekatishwa tamaa','This <a href="%1$s">child theme</a> requires its parent theme, %2$s.'=>'This <a href="%1$s">child theme</a> requires its parent theme, %2$s.','Plugin InstallerFavorites'=>'Vipendwa','To install the theme so you can preview it with your site&#8217;s content and customize its theme options, click the "Install" button at the top of the left-hand pane. The theme files will be downloaded to your website automatically. When this is complete, the theme is now available for activation, which you can do by clicking the "Activate" link, or by navigating to your Manage Themes screen and clicking the "Live Preview" link under any installed theme&#8217;s thumbnail image.'=>'To install the theme so you can preview it with your site&#8217;s content and customize its theme options, click the "Install" button at the top of the left-hand pane. The theme files will be downloaded to your website automatically. When this is complete, the theme is now available for activation, which you can do by clicking the "Activate" link, or by navigating to your Manage Themes screen and clicking the "Live Preview" link under any installed theme&#8217;s thumbnail image.','widgetAdd'=>'Ongeza','widgetEdit'=>'Hariri','Search by tag'=>'Tafuta kutumia lebo','Search by author'=>'Tafuta kutumia jina la mwandishi','Search by keyword'=>'Tafuta kwa neno kuu','Type of search'=>'Aina ya utafutaji','Screen Options Tab'=>'Screen Options Tab','Contextual Help Tab'=>'Contextual Help Tab','Select comment'=>'Chagua maoni','Tags can be selectively converted to categories using the <a href="%s">tag to category converter</a>.'=>'Tags can be selectively converted to categories using the <a href="%s">tag to category converter</a>.','You can delete Link Categories in the Bulk Action pull-down, but that action does not delete the links within the category. Instead, it moves them to the default Link Category.'=>'Unaweza kufuta Sehemu za Kiunganisho kwenye Chaguo cha Wingi wa Wingi, lakini hatua hiyo haifuta viungo vilivyomo kwenye kitengo. Badala yake, inawahamisha kwa Kikundi cha Kiunga cha chaguo-msingi.','You can select an image to be shown at the top of your site by uploading from your computer or choosing from your media library. After selecting an image you will be able to crop it.'=>'Unaweza kuchagua picha ya kuonyeshwa juu ya tovuti yako kwa kupakia kutoka kwa kompyuta yako au kuchagua kutoka maktaba yako ya media. Baada ya kuchagua picha utaweza kuipanda.','Skip to main content'=>'Ruka hadi kwa yaliyomo makuu','You can set a custom image header for your site. Simply upload the image and crop it, and the new header will go live immediately. Alternatively, you can use an image that has already been uploaded to your Media Library by clicking the &#8220;Choose Image&#8221; button.'=>'Unaweza kuweka kichwa cha picha cha kawaida kwa wavuti yako. Pakia picha tu na uipate, na kichwa mpya kitatoka moja kwa moja. Vinginevyo, unaweza kutumia picha ambayo tayari imeshapakiwa kwenye Maktaba yako ya Media kwa kubonyeza kitufe cha &#8220;Chagua Picha.&#8221; ','Skip Cropping, Publish Image as Is'=>'Ruka Kupogoa, Chapisha Picha kama ilivyo','Choose Image'=>'Chagua Picha','Or choose an image from your media library:'=>'Ama chagua picha kutoka kwa maktaba ya midia:','Select Image'=>'Chagua Picha','Collapse'=>'Angusha','If you do not want a header image to be displayed on your site at all, click the &#8220;Remove Header Image&#8221; button at the bottom of the Header Image section of this page. If you want to re-enable the header image later, you just have to select one of the other image options and click &#8220;Save Changes&#8221;.'=>'Ikiwa hutaki picha ya kichwa kuonyeshwa kwenye tovuti yako hata kidogo, bofya &#8220;Ondoa Picha ya Kichwa&#8221; kitufe kilicho chini ya sehemu ya Picha ya Kichwa cha ukurasa huu. Iwapo ungependa kuwezesha upya picha ya kichwa baadaye, itabidi tu uchague moja ya chaguo zingine za picha na ubofye &#8220;Hifadhi Mabadiliko&#8221;.','pluginInstalled'=>'Imesakinishwa','Previewing and Customizing'=>'Kuhakiki na Kubinafsisha','Previewing and Installing'=>'Kuhakiki na Kusakinisha','Once you have generated a list of themes, you can preview and install any of them. Click on the thumbnail of the theme you are interested in previewing. It will open up in a full-screen Preview page to give you a better idea of how that theme will look.'=>'Mara tu unapounda orodha ya mada, unaweza kuhakiki na kusakinisha yoyote kati yao. Bofya kwenye kijipicha cha mandhari ambayo ungependa kuhakiki. Itafunguka katika ukurasa wa Onyesho la kukagua skrini nzima ili kukupa wazo bora la jinsi mandhari hayo yatakavyoonekana.','The Categories and Tags Converter link on this screen will take you to the Import screen, where that Converter is one of the plugins you can install. Once that plugin is installed, the Activate Plugin &amp; Run Importer link will take you to a screen where you can choose to convert tags into categories or vice versa.'=>'Kiungo cha Vitengo na Kubadilisha Tepe kwenye skrini hii kitakupeleka kwa skrini ya Kuingiza, ambapo hicho Kibadilishaji ni mojawapo ya vijalizi ambavyo unaweza kusanukisha. Punde  kijalizi hicho kinaposanukishwa, Wezesha Kijalizi&amp; kiunho cha Anzisha Kiingizaji kitakupeleka kwa skrini ambapo utachagua kubadilisha tepe kuwa vitengo au kinyume chake.','Categories have hierarchy, meaning that you can nest sub-categories. Tags do not have hierarchy and cannot be nested. Sometimes people start out using one on their posts, then later realize that the other would work better for their content.'=>'Categories have hierarchy, meaning that you can nest sub-categories. Tags do not have hierarchy and cannot be nested. Sometimes people start out using one on their posts, then later realize that the other would work better for their content.','For most themes, the header text is your Site Title and Tagline, as defined in the <a href="%s">General Settings</a> section.'=>'Kwa mada nyingi, maandishi ya kichwa ni Kichwa cha Tovuti yako na Tagline, kama inavyofafanuliwa katika sehemu ya <a href="%s">Mipangilio ya Jumla</a>.','If your theme has more than one default header image, or you have uploaded more than one custom header image, you have the option of having WordPress display a randomly different image on each page of your site. Click the &#8220;Random&#8221; radio button next to the Uploaded Images or Default Images section to enable this feature.'=>'Ikiwa mada yako ina picha ya kichwa zaidi ya moja, au umepakia picha zaidi ya moja ya kichwa, una chaguo la kuwa na WordPress kuonyesha picha tofauti kwa kila ukurasa wa tovuti yako. Bonyeza kitufe cha redio isiyo karibu na kando ya Sehemu Iliyopakuliwa ya Picha au Sehemu ya Picha Mbadala ili kuwezesha huduma hii.','Some themes come with additional header images bundled. If you see multiple images displayed, select the one you would like and click the &#8220;Save Changes&#8221; button.'=>'Baadhi ya mandhari huja na picha za ziada za vichwa vilivyounganishwa. Ukiona picha nyingi zimeonyeshwa, chagua moja ungependa na ubofye &#8220;Hifadhi Mabadiliko&#8221; kitufe.','You can choose from the theme&#8217;s default header images, or use one of your own. You can also customize how your Site Title and Tagline are displayed.'=>'Unaweza kuchagua picha za kichwa cha kichwa cha msingi, au utumie moja yako. Unaweza pia kubinafsisha jinsi Kichwa chako cha Tovuti na Tagline zinaonyeshwa.','This screen is used to customize the header section of your theme.'=>'Skrini hii hutumiwa kurekebisha sehemu ya kichwa cha mwonekano wako.','Configuration Error'=>'Hitilafu la Usanidi','Revert to the <strong>Browser Uploader</strong> by clicking the link below the drag and drop box.'=>'Revert to the <strong>Browser Uploader</strong> by clicking the link below the drag and drop box.','User deleted.'=>'Mtumiaji amaefutwa.','Could not copy files. You may have run out of disk space.'=>'Haingeweza kinakili faili. Umeishiwa na nafasi ya diski.','Find a theme based on specific features.'=>'Pata dhima kutegemea vipengele maalum.','Search for themes by keyword.'=>'Tafuta dhima kwa kutumia neno msingi','In all likelihood, these items were supplied to you by your web host. If you do not have this information, then you will need to contact them before you can continue. If you are ready&hellip;'=>'Kwa uwezekano wote, vitu hivi vilitolewa kwako na mwenyeji wako wa wavuti. Ikiwa huna maelezo haya, basi utahitaji kuwasiliana nao kabla ya kuendelea. Ikiwa uko tayari&hellip;','This theme is broken.'=>'Dhima imevunjika','Set as header'=>'Weka kama kijajuu','Set as background'=>'Weka kama mandharinyuma','Customize &#8220;%s&#8221;'=>'Geuza &#8220;%s&#8221;','(required)'=>'(latakikana)','Edit Link'=>'Hariri kiungo','<strong>Error:</strong> This email is already registered. Please choose another one.'=>'<strong>Hitilafu:</strong> Barua pepe hii tayari imesajiliwa. Tafadhali chagua nyingine.','<strong>Error:</strong> Please enter a nickname.'=>'<strong>HITILAFU</strong>: Tafadhali ingiza jina la utani.','https://wordpress.org/about/'=>'https://wordpress.org/about/','Select All'=>'Chagua zote','Public, Sticky'=>'Umma, Nata','Privately Published'=>'Imechapishwa kwa Faragha','Save as Pending'=>'Hifadhi kama Inasubiri','Enter a link URL or click above for presets.'=>'Ingiza URL ya kiunganisho au bonyeza hapo juu kwa vifaa.','Link URL'=>'Anwani la tovuti la kiungo','No comments yet.'=>'Bado hakuna maoni','Version:'=>'Toleo','Collapse Sidebar'=>'Angusha Sidebar','Plugin'=>'Kidude','All'=>'Yote','Word count: %s'=>'Hesabu ya neno: %s','Edit comment'=>'Hariri maoni','Preview:'=>'Hakiki','E-mail'=>'Barua pepe','<strong>The parent theme could not be found.</strong> You will need to install the parent theme, %s, before you can use this child theme.'=>'<strong>Mwonekano mzazi haukuweza kupatikana.</strong> Utahitaji kusanikisha mwonekano mzazi, %s, kabla ya kutumia mwonekano huu mtoto.','Successfully installed the parent theme, <strong>%1$s %2$s</strong>.'=>'Dhima kuu imesakinishwa, <strong>%1$s %2$s</strong>.','The parent theme, <strong>%1$s %2$s</strong>, is currently installed.'=>'Dhima kuu, <strong>%1$s %2$s</strong>, imesakinishwa.','Preparing to install <strong>%1$s %2$s</strong>&#8230;'=>'Inajiandaa kusakinisha <strong>%1$s %2$s</strong>&#8230;','This theme requires a parent theme. Checking if it is installed&#8230;'=>'Dhima inahitaji dhima kuu. Linathibitisha ikiwa imesakinishwa;','Show header text with your image.'=>'Onyesha maandishi ya kichwa na picha yako.','Header Text'=>'Maandishi ya Kichwa','There is a new version of %1$s available. <a href="%2$s" %3$s>View version %4$s details</a> or <a href="%5$s" %6$s>update now</a>.'=>'Kuna toleo jipya %1$s linalopatikana. <a href="%2$s" %3$s>Angalia maelezo ya toleo %4$s</a> au <a href="%5$s" %6$s>sasisha sasa</a>.','By %s.'=>'Kwa %s.','Add Comment'=>'Ongeza maoni','http://ma.tt/'=>'http://ma.tt/','This is not just a plugin, it symbolizes the hope and enthusiasm of an entire generation summed up in two words sung most famously by Louis Armstrong: Hello, Dolly. When activated you will randomly see a lyric from <cite>Hello, Dolly</cite> in the upper right of your admin screen on every page.'=>'Hiki sio kijalizi tu, ni ishara ya tumaini na shauku ya kizazi kizima kilichotajwa kwa maneno mawili yaliyoimbwa sana na Louis Armstrong: Habari, Dolly. Unapowamilishwa utaona kwa bahati nasibu sauti kutoka kwa <cite> Habari, Dolly </cite> kwenye haki ya juu ya skrini yako ya admin kwenye kila ukurasa.','Hello Dolly'=>'Habari Bolly','<strong>Welcome</strong> &mdash; Shows links for some of the most common tasks when setting up a new site.'=>'<strong>Welcome</strong> &mdash; Kinaonyesha viungo vya kazi maarufu unapojenga tovuti mpya.','There is a new version of %1$s available. <a href="%2$s" %3$s>View version %4$s details</a>. <em>Automatic update is unavailable for this theme.</em>'=>'There is a new version of %1$s available. <a href="%2$s" %3$s>View version %4$s details</a>. <em>Automatic update is unavailable for this theme.</em>','HowdyWelcome'=>'Karibu','Delete My Site Permanently'=>'Futa tovuti langu milele.','I\'m sure I want to permanently delete my site, and I am aware I can never get it back or use %s again.'=>'Nina uhakika nataka kutoamilisha tovuti langu, na najua sitaweza kulipata wala kulitumia %s tena.','Remember, once deleted your site cannot be restored.'=>'Tahadhari, ukifuta tovuti lako hautaweza kuirejesha tena.','If you do not want to use your %s site any more, you can delete it using the form below. When you click <strong>Delete My Site Permanently</strong> you will be sent an email with a link in it. Click on this link to delete your site.'=>'Ikiwa hutaki kutumia tovuti yako %s zaidi, unaweza kuifuta kwa kutumia fomu hapa chini. Unapobofya <strong> Futa Tovuti yangu kabisa </strong> utatumiwa barua pepe na kiunga ndani yake. Bonyeza kwenye kiunga hiki ili ufute tovuti yako.','Thank you. Please check your email for a link to confirm your action. Your site will not be deleted until this link is clicked.'=>'Asante. Tafadhali angalia barua pepe kuthibitisha kitendo hiki. Tovuti lako halitafutwa hadi kiungo hiki kibonyezwe.','Sorry, the link you clicked is stale. Please select another option.'=>'Samahani, kiungo ulichobofya hakitumiki. Chagua kingine.','Thank you for using %s, your site has been deleted. Happy trails to you until we meet again.'=>'Asante kwa kutumia %s, tovuti lako limefutwa. Kwaheri hadi tukutane tena.','Primary Site'=>'Tovuti ya msingi','British English'=>'Kiingereza cha Uingereza','American English'=>'Kimarekani','View Site'=>'Tazama tovuti','Visit Dashboard'=>'Tembelea dashibodi','Your Sites'=>'Tovuti lako','If you reached this screen by accident and meant to visit one of your own sites, here are some shortcuts to help you find your way.'=>'Ikiwa ulifikia skrini hii kwa bahati mbaya na ulikusudia kutembelea moja ya tovuti zako, hapa kuna njia za mkato kukusaidia kupata njia yako.','You attempted to access the "%1$s" dashboard, but you do not currently have privileges on this site. If you believe you should be able to access the "%1$s" dashboard, please contact your network administrator.'=>'Ulijaribu kupata dashibodi ya "%1$s", lakini kwa sasa hauna haki kwenye tovuti hii. Ikiwa unaamini unapaswa kufikia dashibodi ya "%1$s", tafadhali wasiliana na msimamizi wa mtandao wako.','MB (Leave blank for network default)'=>'MB (Acha tupu kwa msingi wa mtandao)','[%s] New Admin Email Address'=>'[%s] Anwani ya barua pepe ya Msimamizi Mpya','Disabled'=>'Imezimwa','Paused <span class="count">(%s)</span>'=>'Imesimamishwa <span class="count">(%s)</span>' . "\0" . 'Imesimamishwa <span class="count">(%s)</span>','Global Settings'=>'Mipangilio jumla','You must be a member of at least one site to use this page.'=>'Lazima uwe mwanachama wa angalau tovuti moja kutumia ukurasa huu.','The primary site you chose does not exist.'=>'Tovuti msingi uliochagua halipo.','If you want to run multiple WordPress installations in a single database, change this.'=>'Ukitaka kuendesha sakinisho kadhaa za WordPress kwenye hifadhidata moja, geuza hili:','Table Prefix'=>'Table Prefix','Database Host'=>'Kipangishi cha Hifadhidata','example passwordpassword'=>'nywila','example usernameusername'=>'jina la mtumiaji','Database Name'=>'Jina la hifadhidata','Below you should enter your database connection details. If you are not sure about these, contact your host.'=>'Hapa chini unapaswa kuingiza maelezo yako ya muunganisho wa hifadhidata. Ikiwa huna uhakika kuhusu haya, wasiliana na mwenyeji wako.','Let&#8217;s go!'=>'Tuende!','Table prefix (if you want to run more than one WordPress in a single database)'=>'Table prefix (iwapo unataka kuwa na zaidi ya WordPress moja  kwenye hifadhidata moja)','Database host'=>'Kipangishi cha hifadhidata','Database password'=>'Nywila ya hifadhidata','Database username'=>'Jina la utumizi wa hifadhidata','Database name'=>'Jina la hifadhidata','WordPress &rsaquo; Setup Configuration File'=>'Faili ya Usanidi wa Usanidi wa WordPress','The file %1$s already exists one level above your WordPress installation. If you need to reset any of the configuration items in this file, please delete it first. You may try <a href="%2$s">installing now</a>.'=>'The file %1$s already exists one level above your WordPress installation. If you need to reset any of the configuration items in this file, please delete it first. You may try <a href="%2$s">installing now</a>.','The file %1$s already exists. If you need to reset any of the configuration items in this file, please delete it first. You may try <a href="%2$s">installing now</a>.'=>'The file %1$s already exists. If you need to reset any of the configuration items in this file, please delete it first. You may try <a href="%2$s">installing now</a>.','Sorry, I need a %s file to work from. Please re-upload this file to your WordPress installation.'=>'Samahani, ninahitaji faili %s ili ifanye kazi kutoka. Tafadhali pakia tena faili hii kwenye usanidi wako wa WordPress.','To allow use of this page to automatically repair database problems, please add the following line to your %s file. Once this line is added to your config, reload this page.'=>'Kuruhusu matumizi ya ukurasa huu kukarabati kiatomati shida za hifadhidata, tafadhali ongeza safu ifuatayo kwenye faili yako ya  %s . Mara mstari huu unapoongezwa kwenye usanidi wako, pakia ukurasa huu tena.','No comments awaiting moderation.'=>'Hamna maoni yanasubiri kudhibitiwa.','Plugin installer section titleOther Notes'=>'Vidokezo Vingine','Plugin installer section titleChangelog'=>'Changelog','Plugin installer section titleScreenshots'=>'Picha za skrini','Plugin installer section titleFAQ'=>'Maswali','Plugin installer section titleInstallation'=>'Sakinisho','Plugin installer section titleDescription'=>'Maelezo','Plugin Homepage &#187;'=>'Ukurasa nyumbani ya kidude','You can export a file of your site&#8217;s content in order to import it into another installation or platform. The export file will be an XML file format called WXR. Posts, pages, comments, custom fields, categories, and tags can be included. You can choose for the WXR file to include only certain posts or pages by setting the dropdown filters to limit the export by category, author, date range by month, or publishing status.'=>'Unaweza kuhamisha faili ya yaliyomo kwenye tovuti yako ili kuiingiza kwenye usakinishaji mwingine au jukwaa. Faili ya kuhamisha itakuwa umbizo la faili la XML inayoitwa WXR. Machapisho, kurasa, maoni, uwanja maalum, anuwai, na vitambulisho vinaweza kujumuishwa. Unaweza kuchagua faili ya WXR kujumuisha machapisho au kurasa fulani tu kwa kuweka vichujio vya kushuka ili kupunguza usafirishaji na kitengo, mwandishi, tarehe ya tarehe kwa mwezi, au hali ya kuchapisha.','Failed to repair the %1$s table. Error: %2$s'=>'Imefeli kukarabati %1$s jedwali. Kosa : %2$s','New users will receive an email letting them know they&#8217;ve been added as a user for your site. This email will also contain their password. Check the box if you do not want the user to receive a welcome email.'=>'Watumizi wapya watapokea barua pepe kuwaambia kuwa wameongezwa kama watumizi wa tovuti yako. Barua pepe hii pia itakuwa na nenosiri yao. Angalia kisanduku ikiwa hautaki mtumizi apokee barua pepe ya kukaribishwa.','There are unsaved changes that will be lost. \'OK\' to continue, \'Cancel\' to return to the Image Editor.'=>'Kuna mabadiliko ambayo hajajifadhiwa ambayo yatapotea. \'Sawa\' kuendelea, \'Ghairi\' kurudi kwa Kihariri wa Picha.','Post via email settings allow you to send your WordPress installation an email with the content of your post. You must set up a secret email account with POP3 access to use this, and any mail received at this address will be posted, so it&#8217;s a good idea to keep this address very secret.'=>'Post via email settings allow you to send your WordPress installation an email with the content of your post. You must set up a secret email account with POP3 access to use this, and any mail received at this address will be posted, so it&#8217;s a good idea to keep this address very secret.','You can filter the list of users by User Role using the text links above the users list to show All, Administrator, Editor, Author, Contributor, or Subscriber. The default view is to show all users. Unused User Roles are not listed.'=>'Unaweza kuchuja orodha ya watumiaji na Wajibu wa Mtumiaji kwa kutumia viungo vya maandishi juu ya orodha ya watumiaji kuonyesha Yote, Msimamizi, Mhariri, Mwandishi, Mtoaji, au Msajili. Mtazamo chaguo-msingi ni kuonyesha watumiaji wote. Majukumu ya Mtumiaji yasiyotumika hayakuorodheshwa.','In previous versions of WordPress, all importers were built-in. They have been turned into plugins since most people only use them once or infrequently.'=>'Katika matoleo ya asali ya WordPress, viingizaji vilijengwa ndani. Sasa nimebadilishwa kuwa vijalizi kwa maana watu wengi huvitumia mara moja ama sio kila wakati.','There is an autosave of this post that is more recent than the version below. <a href="%s">View the autosave</a>'=>'Kuna muhtasari wa chapisho hili ambayo ni ya hivi karibuni zaidi kuliko toleo lililo chini. <a href="%s"> Angalia autosave</a>','Image could not be processed. Please go back and try again.'=>'Image could not be processed. Please go back and try again.','The active theme is broken. Reverting to the default theme.'=>'Mwonekano huu umevunjika. Inatekeleza mwonekano msingi.','WordPress can also attempt to optimize the database. This improves performance in some situations. Repairing and optimizing the database can take a long time and the database will be locked while optimizing.'=>'WordPress pia inaweza kujaribu kuboresha hifadhidata. Hii inaboresha utendaji katika hali zingine. Kukarabati na kuongeza database kunaweza kuchukua muda mrefu na hifadhidata itafungwa wakati wa kuwezesha.','WordPress can automatically look for some common database problems and repair them. Repairing can take a while, so please be patient.'=>'WordPress inaweza kutafuta moja kwa moja shida kadhaa za kawaida za hifadhidata na kuzirekebisha. Kurekebisha inaweza kuchukua muda, kwa hivyo tafadhali kuwa na subira.','Repairs complete. Please remove the following line from wp-config.php to prevent this page from being used by unauthorized users.'=>'Marekebisho yamekamilika. Tafadhali ondoa laini ifuatayo kutoka wp-config.php kuzuia ukurasa huu kutumiwa na watumizi wasioidhinishwa.','The %1$s table is not okay. It is reporting the following error: %2$s. WordPress will attempt to repair this table&hellip;'=>'Jedwali la %1$s sio sawa. Inaripoti makosa yafuatayo: %2$s. WordPress itajaribu kukarabati jedwali hili$hellip:','Enter the email address or username of an existing user on this network to invite them to this site. That person will be sent an email asking them to confirm the invite.'=>'Ingiza anwani ya barua pepe au jina la mtumizi la mtumizi aliyepo kwenye mtandao huu kuwaalika kwenye wavuti hii. Mtu huyo atatumiwa barua pepe kumwuuliza kuthibitisha mwaliko.','Enter the email address of an existing user on this network to invite them to this site. That person will be sent an email asking them to confirm the invite.'=>'Ingiza anwani ya barua pepe ya mtumiaji aliyepo kwenye mtandao huu ili uwaalike kwenye tovuti hii. Mtu huyo atatumwa barua pepe kuwauliza kuthibitisha mwaliko.','Show Toolbar when viewing site'=>'Onyesha upauzana unapoangalia tovuti','For more information, see <a href="%s">the release notes</a>.'=>'Kwa habari zaidi, angalia <a href="%s">vidokezo vya utoaji</a>.','<strong>Version %1$s</strong> addressed some security issues and fixed %2$s bug.'=>'<strong>Toleo%1$s</strong> liliangazia maswala ya usalama fulani na kurekebisha bug ya %2$s.' . "\0" . '<strong>Toleo%1$s</strong> liliangazia maswala ya usalama fulani na kurekebisha bugs za %2$s.','<strong>Version %1$s</strong> addressed a security issue and fixed %2$s bug.'=>'<strong>Toleo%1$s</strong> liliangazia swala la usalama fulani na kurekebisha bug ya %2$s.' . "\0" . '<strong>Toleo%1$s</strong> liliangazia swala la usalama fulani na kurekebisha bug ya %2$s.','<strong>Version %1$s</strong> addressed %2$s bug.'=>'<strong>Tiles la %1$s</strong> liliangazia bug %2$s.' . "\0" . '<strong>Tiles la %1$s</strong> liliangazia bugs %2$s.','<strong>Version %s</strong> addressed some security issues.'=>'<strong>Toleo %s</strong> limeshughulikia maswala fulani  ya usalama.','Maintenance and Security Release'=>'Toleo la Usalama na Utengenezaji','Security Release'=>'Toleo la Usalama','Maintenance Release'=>'Toleo la Utengenezaji','What&#8217;s New'=>'Nini kipya','This screen allows you to choose your permalink structure. You can choose from common settings or create custom URL structures.'=>'Skrini hii hukuruhusu kuchagua muundo wako wa kiungo-dumu. Unaweza kuchagua kutoka kwa mipangilio ya kawaida au kuunda muundo wa URL maalum.','Welcome to WordPress %1$s. <a href="%2$s">Learn more</a>.'=>'Karibu WordPress %1$s. <a href="%2$s">Kwa mingi zaidi</a>.','You can upload media files here without creating a post first. This allows you to upload files to use with posts and pages later and/or to get a web link for a particular file that you can share. There are three options for uploading files:'=>'Unaweza kupakia faili za midia hapa bila kuunda chapisho la kwanza. Hii hukuruhusu kupakia faili za kutumia na machapisho na kurasa baadaye na / au kupata kiunga cha wavuti kwa faili fulani ambayo unaweza kushiriki. Kuna chaguzi tatu za kupakia faili:','Adding Tags'=>'Inaongeza lebo','Adding Categories'=>'Inaongeza vikundi','Troubleshooting'=>'Inatatua','How to Update'=>'Jinsi ya kusasisha','Once you&#8217;ve saved the download file, you can use the Import function in another WordPress installation to import the content from this site.'=>'Mara tu baada ya kuhifadhi faili ya kupakua, unaweza kutumia kazi ya Kuagiza katika usakinishaji mwingine wa WordPress kuagiza yaliyomo kutoka kwa wavuti hii.','Attaching Files'=>'Inaambatisha faili','You can also edit or move multiple posts to the Trash at once. Select the posts you want to act on using the checkboxes, then select the action you want to take from the Bulk actions menu and click Apply.'=>'Unaweza pia kuhariri au kusongeza machapisho mengi kwenye takataka mara moja. Chagua machapisho unayotaka kuchukua kwa kutumia kisanduku cha ukaguzi, kisha uchague hatua unayotaka kuchukua kutoka kwa menyu ya Vitendo vya Wingi na ubonyeze Tekeleza.','Available Actions'=>'Vitendo zilizopo','You can customize the display of this screen&#8217;s contents in a number of ways:'=>'Unaweza kugeuza muonekano wa maudhui ya skrini hii kwa njia tofauti:','Screen Content'=>'Maudhui ya skrini','This screen provides access to all of your posts. You can customize the display of this screen to suit your workflow.'=>'This screen provides access to all of your posts. You can customize the display of this screen to suit your workflow.','If the importer you need is not listed, <a href="%s">search the plugin directory</a> to see if an importer is available.'=>'Ikiwa kiingizaji unachohitaji hakijaorodheshwa, <a href="%s"> tafuta saraka ya kijalizi </a> kuona ikiwa kiingizaji vitu kinapatikana.','Moderating Comments'=>'Dhibitisha Maoni','If you want to convert your categories to tags (or vice versa), use the <a href="%s">Categories and Tags Converter</a> available from the Import screen.'=>'Ikiwa unataka kubadilisha vikundi vyako kuwa tepe (au kinyume chake), tumia Sehemu za <a href="%s">Kibadili Makundi na Tepe</a> kilicho kwenye Skrini ya Kuingiza.','Adding Plugins'=>'Inaongeza vidude','Adding Themes'=>'Inaongeza dhima','Subscribers can read comments/comment/receive newsletters, etc. but cannot create regular site content.'=>'Subscribers can read comments/comment/receive newsletters, etc. but cannot create regular site content.','Authors can publish and manage their own posts, and are able to upload files.'=>'Waandishi wanaweza kuchapisha na kusimamia machapisho yao, na pia wanaweza kupakia faili.','Here is a basic overview of the different user roles and the permissions associated with each one:'=>'Here is a basic overview of the different user roles and the permissions associated with each one:','User Roles'=>'Jukumu la watumiaji','Custom Structures'=>'Miundo misingi','Common Settings'=>'Mipangilio ya kawaida','Permalinks are the permanent URLs to your individual pages and blog posts, as well as your category and tag archives. A permalink is the web address used to link to your content. The URL to each post should be permanent, and never change &#8212; hence the name permalink.'=>'Viungodumu ni URLs za kudumu kwa kurasa zako za kibinafsi na machapisho ya blogi, na pia kikundi chako na kumbukumbu za tepe. Kiungodumu ni anwani ya tovuti inayotumika kuunganisha yaliyomo. URL kwa kila chapisho inapaswa kuwa ya kudumu, na kamwe ibadilike kwa kicho kiungodumu.','You can submit content in several different ways; this screen holds the settings for all of them. The top section controls the editor within the dashboard, while the rest control external publishing methods. For more information on any of these methods, use the documentation links.'=>'You can submit content in several different ways; this screen holds the settings for all of them. The top section controls the editor within the dashboard, while the rest control external publishing methods. For more information on any of these methods, use the documentation links.','Uploading Files allows you to choose the folder and path for storing your uploaded files.'=>'Kupakia Faili hukuruhusu kuchagua folda na njia ya kuhifadhi faili zako zilizopakiwa.','Installing themes on Multisite can only be done from the Network Admin section.'=>'Kusanukisha mionekano kwenye Multisite kunaweza tu kufanywa kutoka kwa sehemu ya Msimamizi wa Mtandao.','If desired, WordPress will automatically alert various services of your new posts.'=>'Ukipenda, WordPress linaweza kuwafahamisha moja kwa mojai huduma tofauti kuhusu machapisho yako mpya.','Post Via Email'=>'Chapisha kupitia barua pepe','This screen provides many options for controlling the management and display of comments and links to your posts/pages. So many, in fact, they will not all fit here! :) Use the documentation links to get information on what each discussion setting does.'=>'Skrini hii inakupatia chaguo nyingi za kudhibiti usimamizi na uonyeshaji wa maoni na viungo vya machapisho/kurasa zako. Chaguo hizi ni nyingi haziwezi toshea hapa! :) Tumia viungo vya nyaraka ili kupata taarifa juu ya kile kila mpangilio wa majadiliano hufanya.','You can change your password, turn on keyboard shortcuts, change the color scheme of your WordPress administration screens, and turn off the WYSIWYG (Visual) editor, among other things. You can hide the Toolbar (formerly called the Admin Bar) from the front end of your site, however it cannot be disabled on the admin screens.'=>'You can change your password, turn on keyboard shortcuts, change the color scheme of your WordPress administration screens, and turn off the WYSIWYG (Visual) editor, among other things. You can hide the Toolbar (formerly called the Admin Bar) from the front end of your site, however it cannot be disabled on the admin screens.','This sidebar is no longer available and does not show anywhere on your site. Remove each of the widgets below to fully remove this inactive sidebar.'=>'Huu mwambaa upande haupatikani kwa sasa na hauonyeshi popote kwenye tovuti lako. Ondoa kila wijeti ilioko hapa chini ili pia kuondoa mwambaa upandee huu amabao siamilifu.','Inactive Sidebar (not used)'=>'Mwambaa upande (siamilifu)','Clicking <strong>Select Files</strong> opens a navigation window showing you files in your operating system. Selecting <strong>Open</strong> after clicking on the file you want activates a progress bar on the uploader screen.'=>'Clicking <strong>Select Files</strong> opens a navigation window showing you files in your operating system. Selecting <strong>Open</strong> after clicking on the file you want activates a progress bar on the uploader screen.','<strong>Drag and drop</strong> your files into the area below. Multiple files are allowed.'=>'<strong> Buruta na kuacha</strong> faili zako kwenye eneo lililo chini. Faili nyingi zinaruhusiwa.','You can assign keywords to your posts using <strong>tags</strong>. Unlike categories, tags have no hierarchy, meaning there is no relationship from one tag to another.'=>'Unaweza kugawa maneno kwa machapisho yako kwa kutumia <strong>tepe</strong>. Tofauti na vikundi, tepe hazina ngazi za ukubwa, kwa maana hakuna uhusiano kutoka tepe moja kwenda nyingine.','You can create groups of links by using Link Categories. Link Category names must be unique and Link Categories are separate from the categories you use for posts.'=>'Unaweza kuhuluku vikundi kwa kutumia vyundo vya vikundi. Majina za vyungo vya vikundi ni lazima ziwe za kiepekee na vyungo vya vikundi ni tofauti vikundi unavyotumia kwenye machapisho.','Missing Widgets'=>'Wijeti hazipo','Removing and Reusing'=>'Kuondosha na kutumia tena','If a media file has not been attached to any content, you will see that in the Uploaded To column, and can click on Attach to launch a small popup that will allow you to search for existing content and attach the file.'=>'Ikiwa faili ya midia haijaiambatishwa na yaliyomo yoyote, utaona kuwa kwenye safu Iliyopakiwa, na unaweza kubonyeza Ambatisha ili kuzindua kidukizo kidogo ambacho kitakuruhusu kutafuta yaliyomo na ambatisha faili.','All the files you&#8217;ve uploaded are listed in the Media Library, with the most recent uploads listed first. You can use the Screen Options tab to customize the display of this screen.'=>'Faili zote ulizozipakia zimeorodheshwa kwenye Maktaba ya Midia, na upakiaji wa hivi karibuni ulioorodheshwa kwanza. Unaweza kutumia tabo Chaguzi za Screen ili kubadilisha maonyesho ya skrini hii.','You can also perform the same types of actions, including narrowing the list by using the filters, acting on a page using the action links that appear when you hover over a row, or using the Bulk actions menu to edit the metadata for multiple pages at once.'=>'Unaweza pia kufanya aina kama hizo za vitendo, pamoja na kupunguza orodha kwa kutumia vichungi, kaimu kwenye ukurasa ukitumia viungo vya kitendaji ambavyo hujitokeza wakati unazunguka kwa safu, au kwa kutumia menyu ya Vitendo vya Wingi kuhariri metadata ya kurasa nyingi kwa mara moja.','Managing pages is very similar to managing posts, and the screens can be customized in the same way.'=>'Kumeneji ukurasa ni kama kumeneji machapisho, na skrini  zinageuzwa kwa njia kwa njia zinazofanana.','Pages are similar to posts in that they have a title, body text, and associated metadata, but they are different in that they are not part of the chronological blog stream, kind of like permanent posts. Pages are not categorized or tagged, but can have a hierarchy. You can nest pages under other pages by making one the &#8220;Parent&#8221; of the other, creating a group of pages.'=>'Pages are similar to posts in that they have a title, body text, and associated metadata, but they are different in that they are not part of the chronological blog stream, kind of like permanent posts. Pages are not categorized or tagged, but can have a hierarchy. You can nest pages under other pages by making one the &#8220;Parent&#8221; of the other, creating a group of pages.','Many people take advantage of keyboard shortcuts to moderate their comments more quickly. Use the link to the side to learn more.'=>'Watu wengi hutumia njia mkato ya kibodi ili kustani machapisho kwa haraka. Tumia kiungo iliyoko kando kujua mengi zaidi.','In the <strong>Author</strong> column, in addition to the author&#8217;s name, email address, and site URL, the commenter&#8217;s IP address is shown. Clicking on this link will show you all the comments made from this IP address.'=>'Katika safu ya <strong>Mwandishi</strong>, pamoja na jina la mwandishi, anwani ya barua pepe, na URL ya tovuti, anwani ya IP ya mtoa maoni inaonyeshwa. Kubofya kiungo hiki kutakuonyesha maoni yote yaliyotolewa kutoka kwa anwani hii ya IP.','You can manage comments made on your site similar to the way you manage posts and other content. This screen is customizable in the same ways as other management screens, and you can act on comments using the on-hover action links or the bulk actions.'=>'Unaweza kudhibiti maoni yaliyotolewa kwenye wavuti yako sawa na jinsi unavyosimamia machapisho na yaliyomo mengine. Skrini hii inaweza kuboreshwa kwa njia zile zile za skrini zingine za usimamizi, na unaweza kuchukua hatua kwenye maoni ukitumia viungo vya kitendaji au hatua za Wingi.','Links in the Toolbar at the top of the screen connect your dashboard and the front end of your site, and provide access to your profile and helpful WordPress information.'=>'Links in the Toolbar at the top of the screen connect your dashboard and the front end of your site, and provide access to your profile and helpful WordPress information.','Deleting Links'=>'Kufutwa kwa viungo','Links may be separated into Link Categories; these are different than the categories used on your posts.'=>'Links may be separated into Link Categories; these are different than the categories used on your posts.','<a href="%1$s">Learn more about WordPress %2$s</a>.'=>'<a href="%1$s">Jifunze zaidi kuhusu WordPress %2$s</a>.','<strong>Edit</strong> takes you to the editable profile screen for that user. You can also reach that screen by clicking on the username.'=>'<strong>Edit</strong> takes you to the editable profile screen for that user. You can also reach that screen by clicking on the username.','Hovering over a row in the users list will display action links that allow you to manage users. You can perform the following actions:'=>'Hovering over a row in the users list will display action links that allow you to manage users. You can perform the following actions:','You can view all posts made by a user by clicking on the number under the Posts column.'=>'Unaweza kuangalia machapisho yote ya mwandishi kwa kubofya nambari zilizopo chini ya safuwima ya machapisho','You can hide/display columns based on your needs and decide how many users to list per screen using the Screen Options tab.'=>'Unaweza kujificha / kuonyesha safuwima kulingana na mahitaji yako na kuamua ni watumiaji wangapi waorodhesha kwa skrini moja kwa kutumia tabo Chaguzi za Screen.','Managing Pages'=>'Kumeneji kurasa','<strong>Preview</strong> will show you what your draft post will look like if you publish it. View will take you to your live site to view the post. Which link is available depends on your post&#8217;s status.'=>'<strong> Hakiki </strong> itakuonyesha jinsi chapisho lako la rasimu litaonekana ulichapisha. Mtazamo itakuchukua kwa tovuti yako ya moja kwa moja kutazama chapisho. Kiunga gani kinapatikana kulingana na hali ya chapisho lako.','<strong>Trash</strong> removes your post from this list and places it in the Trash, from which you can permanently delete it.'=>'<strong> Tupio </strong> huondoa chapisho lako kutoka kwenye orodha hii na kuiweka kwenye takataka, ambayo unaweza kuifuta kabisa.','<strong>Quick Edit</strong> provides inline access to the metadata of your post, allowing you to update post details without leaving this screen.'=>'<strong> Hariri Haraka </strong> inapeana ufikiaji wa ndani ya metadata ya chapisho lako, hukuruhusu kusasisha maelezo ya chapisho bila kuacha skrini hii.','<strong>Edit</strong> takes you to the editing screen for that post. You can also reach that screen by clicking on the post title.'=>'<strong>Hariri</strong> itakupeleka kwenye skrini ya kuhariri. Unaweza kufikia skrini hiyo kwa kubofya kichwa cha chapisho.','Because this is a multisite installation, you may add accounts that already exist on the Network by specifying a username or email, and defining a role. For more options, such as specifying a password, you have to be a Network Administrator and use the hover link under an existing user&#8217;s name to Edit the user profile under Network Admin > All Users.'=>'Kwa sababu huu ni usanidi wa aina nyingi, unaweza kuongeza akaunti ambazo tayari zipo kwenye Mtandao kwa kutaja jina la mtumiaji au barua pepe, na kuelezea jukumu. Kwa chaguzi zaidi, kama vile kutaja nywila, lazima uwe Msimamizi wa Mtandao na utumie kiunga cha hover chini ya jina la mtumiaji uliopo Kubadilisha wasifu wa mtumiaji chini ya Msimamizi wa Mtandao> Watumiaji wote.','Go to Dashboard &rarr; Home'=>'Enda kwa Deshbodi &rarr; Nyumbani','Go to Dashboard &rarr; Updates'=>'Rudi kwenye deshbodi &rarr; Sakinisho','Profile updated.'=>'Wasifu umesasishwa','Hi,

You\'ve been invited to join \'%1$s\' at
%2$s with the role of %3$s.

Please click the following link to confirm the invite:
%4$s'=>'Vipi,

Umealikwa kujiunga na \'%1$s\' at
