a','<strong>Random:</strong> Show a different image on each page.'=>'<strong> Bila mpangilio: </strong> Onyesha picha tofauti kwenye kila ukurasa.','You have specified this user for deletion:'=>'Umemteua mtumiaji huyu wa kufutwa:','%s Page Template'=>'%s Kiolezo cha Ukurasa','You cannot delete a plugin while it is active on the main site.'=>'Huwezi kufuta kidude ikiwa amilifu kwenye tovuti kuu.','This plugin may be active on other sites in the network.'=>'Kidude hiki kinaweza kuwa ni amilifu kwenye tovuti zingine kwenye mtandao.','Default Post Format'=>'Mfumo msingi wa Chapisho','Any edits to files from this screen will be reflected on all sites in the network.'=>'Hariri yoyote kwa faili kutoka skrini hii itaonyeshwa kwenye tovuti zote kwenye mtandao.','This screen lists all the existing users for your site. Each user has one of five defined roles as set by the site admin: Site Administrator, Editor, Author, Contributor, or Subscriber. Users with roles other than Administrator will see fewer options in the dashboard navigation when they are logged in, based on their role.'=>'Skrini hii inaorodhesha watumiaji wote waliopo wa tovuti yako. Kila mtumiaji ana moja ya majukumu matano yaliyofafanuliwa kama ilivyowekwa na msimamizi wa wavuti: Msimamizi wa Tovuti, Mhariri, Mwandishi, Mtoaji, au Msajili. Watumiaji walio na majukumu mengine zaidi ya Msimamizi wataona chaguzi chache katika urambazaji wa dashibodi wakati wameingia, kwa kuzingatia jukumu lao.','If you want to make changes but do not want them to be overwritten when the plugin is updated, you may be ready to think about writing your own plugin. For information on how to edit plugins, write your own from scratch, or just better understand their anatomy, check out the links below.'=>'Ikiwa ungependa kufanya mabadiliko lakini hutaki yaandikwe tena wakati programu-jalizi inasasishwa, unaweza kuwa tayari kufikiria kuandika programu-jalizi yako mwenyewe. Kwa habari juu ya jinsi ya kuhariri programu-jalizi, andika yako mwenyewe kutoka mwanzo, au uelewe vyema anatomy yao, angalia viungo vilivyo hapa chini.','The boxes on your Dashboard screen are:'=>'Visanduku vilivyoko kwenye skrini ya deshbodi ni:','sample-page'=>'ukurasa-sampuli','Sample Page'=>'Ukurasa sampuli','Retro (Generated)'=>'Retro (Imezalishwa)','You only have one theme enabled for this site right now. Visit the Network Admin to <a href="%s">enable</a> more themes.'=>'Una mandhari moja pekee iliyowezeshwa kwa tovuti hii kwa sasa. Tembelea Msimamizi wa Mtandao ili <a href="%s">kuwasha</a> mandhari zaidi.','You only have one theme enabled for this site right now. Visit the Network Admin to <a href="%1$s">enable</a> or <a href="%2$s">install</a> more themes.'=>'You only have one theme enabled for this site right now. Visit the Network Admin to <a href="%1$s">enable</a> or <a href="%2$s">install</a> more themes.','You only have one theme installed right now. Live a little! You can choose from over 1,000 free themes in the WordPress Theme Directory at any time: just click on the <a href="%s">Install Themes</a> tab above.'=>'You only have one theme installed right now. Live a little! You can choose from over 1,000 free themes in the WordPress Theme Directory at any time: just click on the <a href="%s">Install Themes</a> tab above.','One or more database tables are unavailable. To allow WordPress to attempt to repair these tables, press the &#8220;Repair Database&#8221; button. Repairing can take a while, so please be patient.'=>'One or more database tables are unavailable. To allow WordPress to attempt to repair these tables, press the &#8220;Repair Database&#8221; button. Repairing can take a while, so please be patient.','Visual Editor RTL Stylesheet'=>'Mtindo ya Kihariri cha Kuonekana','This is a file in your current parent theme.'=>'Hii ni faili kwenye dhima zazi lako.','This child theme inherits templates from a parent theme, %s.'=>'Mwonekano huu wa mtoto unarithi templeti kutoka kwa mwonekano wa mzazi, %s.','Network Enable'=>'Wezesha Mtandao','Your WordPress database has been successfully updated!'=>'Hifadhidata lako la WordPress limesasishwa!','Update Complete'=>'Sasisho limekamilika','Update WordPress Database'=>'Sasisha hifadhidata la WordPress','The database update process may take a little while, so please be patient.'=>'Sasisho la hifadhidata linaweza kuchukuwa muda,kwa hivyo tunakuomba uwe na subira.','Database Update Required'=>'Sasisho la hifadhidata linahitajika','No Update Required'=>'Sasisho halihitajiki','WordPress &rsaquo; Update'=>'WordPress &rsaquo; Usasisho','You are about to install WordPress %s <strong>in English (US)</strong>. There is a chance this update will break your translation. You may prefer to wait for the localized version to be released.'=>'Unakaribia kusanikisha WordPress %s <strong> kwa Kiingereza (Amerika). </strong> Kuna uwezekano kuwa sasisho hili litavunja tafsiri yako. Unaweza kupendelea kungojea toleo la ujanibishaji litolewe.','There is a new version of %1$s available. <a href="%2$s" %3$s>View version %4$s details</a>. <em>Automatic update is unavailable for this plugin.</em>'=>'Kuna toleo jipya la %1$s linalopatikana. <a href="%2$s" %3$s> tazama Toleo maelezo %4$s </a>. <em> Sasisho la otomatiki haipatikani kwa kijalizi hiki. </em>','Update Theme'=>'Sasisha dhima','Update Plugin'=>'Sasisha kidude','Theme updated successfully.'=>'Dhima limesasishwa','Theme update failed.'=>'Usasisho wa dhima imefeli.','Plugin updated successfully.'=>'Kidude kimesasishwa.','Plugin update failed.'=>'Usasisho wa kidude imefeli.','Update package not available.'=>'Kifurushi cha kusasisha halipo.','Date range:'=>'Masafa ya tarehe:','Authors:'=>'Waandishi:','This will contain all of your posts, pages, comments, custom fields, terms, navigation menus, and custom posts.'=>'Hii itakuwa na chapisho zako zote, kurasa, maoni, uwanja maalum, masharti, menyu ya urambazaji, na machapisho maalum.','All content'=>'Maudhui yote','Choose what to export'=>'Chagua cha kuhamisha','commentsMine <span class="count">(%s)</span>'=>'Yangu <span class="count">(%s)</span>' . "\0" . 'Yangu <span class="count">(%s)</span>','%s &#8212; WordPress'=>'%s &#8212; WordPress','column nameIn Response To'=>'Kwa kujibu...','The Available Widgets section contains all the widgets you can choose from. Once you drag a widget into a sidebar, it will open to allow you to configure its settings. When you are happy with the widget settings, click the Save button and the widget will go live on your site. If you click Delete, it will remove the widget.'=>'Sehemu inayopatikana ya Widgets ina widgets unaweza kuchagua kutoka. Mara tu ukivuta vilivyoandikwa kwenye kando ya pembeni, itafunguliwa kukuruhusu usanidi mipangilio yake. Unapofurahi na mipangilio ya widget, bonyeza kitufe cha Hifadhi na widget itaenda moja kwa moja kwenye tovuti yako. Ukibonyeza Futa, itaondoa widget.','Remember to click Update to save metadata entered or changed.'=>'Kumbuka kubonyeza Sasisha Media ili kuokoa metadata iliyoingizwa au iliyobadilishwa.','Note that you crop the image by clicking on it (the Crop icon is already selected) and dragging the cropping frame to select the desired part. Then click Save to retain the cropping.'=>'Kumbuka kuwa unacrop picha hiyo kwa kubonyeza juu yake (ikoni ya Mazao imekwisha kuchaguliwa) na kuvuta sura ya upandaji kuchagua sehemu unayotaka. Kisha bonyeza Hifadhi ili kuhifadhi hali hiyo.','For images only, you can click on Edit Image under the thumbnail to expand out an inline image editor with icons for cropping, rotating, or flipping the image as well as for undoing and redoing. The boxes on the right give you more options for scaling the image, for cropping it, and for cropping the thumbnail in a different way than you crop the original image. You can click on Help in those boxes to get more information.'=>'For images only, you can click on Edit Image under the thumbnail to expand out an inline image editor with icons for cropping, rotating, or flipping the image as well as for undoing and redoing. The boxes on the right give you more options for scaling the image, for cropping it, and for cropping the thumbnail in a different way than you crop the original image. You can click on Help in those boxes to get more information.','This screen allows you to edit fields for metadata in a file within the media library.'=>'Skrini hii hukuruhusu kuhariri sehemu tano za metadata katika faili ndani ya maktaba ya midia.','Email or Username'=>'Anwani ama jina ya utumizi','Search installed themes'=>'Tafuta mada zilizosakinishwa','<strong>Please Note:</strong> Any customizations you have made to theme files will be lost. Please consider using <a href="%s">child themes</a> for modifications.'=>'<strong> Tafadhali kumbuka: </strong> Urekebishaji wowote ambao umefanya kwa faili za mandhari utapotea. Tafadhali fikiria kutumia mada za <a href="%s"> mwonekano mtoto</a> kwa maboreshaji.','postsSticky <span class="count">(%s)</span>'=>'Kisichosongea <span class="count">(%s)</span>' . "\0" . 'Visivyosongea <span class="count">(%s)</span>','Check again.'=>'Angalia tena','Last checked on %1$s at %2$s.'=>'Mara ya mwisho kuangaliwa ni mnamo %1$s saa %2$s.','Please select one or more plugins to update.'=>'Tafadhali chagua kidude moja au zaidi kusasisha.','Please select one or more themes to update.'=>'Tafadhali chagua dhima ama zaidi kusasisha.','The update process is starting. This process may take a while on some hosts, so please be patient.'=>'Mchakato wa kusasisha umeanza. Mchakato huu unaweza kuchukua masaa kwenye vipangishi vingine, kuwa na mwenye subira.','Apply Filters'=>'Weka Vichujio','Editor Style'=>'Mfumo wa uhariri','To perform the requested action, WordPress needs to access your web server.'=>'Ili kutekeleza tendo liliyombwa, WordPress itahitaji kufikia seva yako ya tovuti.','Current Page'=>'Ukurasa Uliofunguliwa','No themes match your request.'=>'Hakuna mionekano inaendana na ombi lako.','Search Sites'=>'Tafuta tovuti','Create a 